%20turned%20to%20India%20to%20secure%20critical%20electronic%20supplies%20and%20sensitive%20goods%2C%20according%20to%20leaked%20documents%20cited%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2F101afcd6-8e6f-4b5f-89b0-98f48cd5d119%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFinancial%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20October%202022%2C%20Russia's%20industry%20and%20trade%20ministry%20made%20plans%20to%20spend%20around%20%241%20billion%20worth%20of%20Indian%20rupees%20on%20trade%20channels%20that%20would%20operate%20outside%20Western%20scrutiny%2C%20the%20outlet%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20FT%2C%20the%20project%20was%20disclosed%20in%20letters%20sent%20to%20a%20shadowy%20trade%20group%20with%20ties%20to%20Moscow's%20secret%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20organization%20%E2%80%94%20the%20Consortium%20for%20Foreign%20Economic%20Activity%20and%20International%20Interstate%20Cooperation%20in%20Industry%20%E2%80%94%20was%20asked%20to%20develop%20a%20plan%20on%20how%20to%20source%20critical%20electronic%20components%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECentral%20to%20these%20efforts%20was%20Russia's%20massive%20trove%20of%20Indian%20rupees.%20As%20Western%20sanctions%20bore%20down%20on%20Moscow%20for%20its%20war%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20Russia%20was%20left%20unable%20to%20repatriate%20rupee%20profits%20from%20its%20ballooning%20oil%20trade%20with%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20summer%20of%20last%20year%2C%20the%20Kremlin%20was%20amassing%20as%20much%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdedollarization-russia-dollar-yuan-billions-india-struggle-use-ruble-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%241%20billion%20worth%20of%20rupees%20per%20month%3C%2Fa%3E%20without%20a%20way%20to%20convert%20or%20spend%20the%20currency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Consortium's%20plan%20offered%20some%20way%20out%2C%20FT%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnder%20its%20scheme%2C%20rupees%20would%20be%20spent%20to%20secure%20dual-use%20components%20through%20a%20%26quot%3Bclosed%20payment%20system%26quot%3B%20between%20Russian%20and%20Indian%20firms%2C%20the%20outlet%20cited.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20would%20provide%20a%20steady%20inflow%20of%20electronic%20equipment%20originally%20bought%20in%20Western%20markets%2C%20the%20leaked%20letters%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFurther%20funds%20could%20be%20directed%20toward%20investments%20in%20Indian%20electronic%20factories%2C%20that%20would%20provide%20Russia%20with%20needed%20information%20infrastructure%2C%20FT%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20it's%20unclear%20how%20much%20of%20this%20plan%20went%20into%20effect%2C%20customs%20data%20tracked%20by%20FT%20align%20with%20the%20operation's%20goals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20the%20leaked%20correspondence%20outlined%20that%20rupees%20would%20be%20used%20on%20electronics%20and%20machinery%20purchases%20from%20India%20%E2%80%94%20since%20mid-2022%2C%20trade%20has%20soared%20steeply%20in%20these%20categories.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeparately%2C%20an%20Indian%20businessman%20with%20knowledge%20of%20the%20matter%20told%20the%20FT%20that%20Russia%20has%20since%20looked%20into%20creating%20facilities%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20Kremlin%2C%20continued%20access%20to%20electronic%20components%20is%20imperative%20as%20Russia's%20fighting%20in%20Ukraine%20drags%20on%20through%20its%20third%20year.%20Since%202022%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-economy-growth-recession-labor-worker-shortage-inflation-sanctions-west-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esanctions%20have%20grown%20much%20tighter%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20gradually%20cutting%20off%20Russia's%20access%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-economy-all-china-banks-refuse-yuan-ruble-transfers-sanctions-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ekey%20financial%20lifelines%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bus