3EElle%20Macpherson%3C%2Fa%3E%20revealed%20that%20she%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20breast%20cancer%20seven%20years%20ago.%20Doctors%20said%20subsequent%20news%20reports%20that%20she%20was%20in%20remission%20because%20of%20alternative%20therapies%20were%20potentially%20misleading%20and%20dangerous.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMacpherson%2C%2060%2C%20who%20is%20also%20the%20founder%20of%20wellness%20company%20WelleCo%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.womensweekly.com.au%2Fnews%2Felle-macpherson-now%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Australian%20Women's%20Weekly%20magazine%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20an%20interview%20published%20on%20Monday%20that%20she%20is%20in%20remission%20from%20breast%20cancer%20despite%20refusing%20the%20conventional%20treatments%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-preventative-chemotherapy-how-it-works-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echemotherapy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20mastectomy%2C%20radiation%2C%20and%20hormonal%20therapy%20her%20doctor%20suggested.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20instead%20opted%20for%20what%20she%20described%20as%20%26quot%3Ban%20intuitive%2C%20heart-led%2C%20holistic%20approach.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMacpherson%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BIn%20traditional%20terms%2C%20they'd%20say%20I'm%20in%20clinical%20remission%2C%20but%20I%20would%20say%20I'm%20in%20utter%20wellness.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENews%20outlets%20around%20the%20world%20reported%20that%20Macpherson%20overcame%20cancer%20with%20alternative%20therapies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Macpherson%20told%20the%20outlet%20that%20she%20had%20a%20lumpectomy%2C%20a%20conventional%20treatment%20that%20removes%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbreast-cancer-risk-screening-age-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebreast%20cancer%20%3C%2Fa%3Ealong%20with%20a%20small%20amount%20of%20the%20healthy%20tissue%20surrounding%20it.%20This%20led%20to%20her%202017%20diagnosis%20of%20a%20type%20of%20breast%20cancer%20known%20as%20HER2-positive%20estrogen-receptive%20intraductal%20carcinoma.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223cf33fad-0891-45c4-96b5-dd9ce951ecbd%5C%22%3EMacpherson's%20lumpectomy%20might%20have%20treated%20her%20breast%20cancer%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20lumpectomy%20in%20itself%20can%20be%20an%20appropriate%20standard%20medical%20treatment%20for%20the%20condition%2C%20professor%20Chris%20Pyke%2C%20a%20cancer%20surgeon%2C%20breast%20cancer%20risk%20quantification%20expert%2C%20and%20the%20director%20of%20medical%20services%20at%20the%20Mater%20private%20hospitals%20in%20Brisbane%2C%20Australia%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fsociety%2Farticle%2F2024%2Fsep%2F04%2Felle-macpherson-breast-cancer-treatment-australian-womens-weekly-misinformation-risk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20The%20Guardian.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPyke%20added%20that%20Macpherson's%20form%20of%20cancer%2C%20in%20many%20cases%2C%20could%20more%20accurately%20be%20described%20as%20a%20type%20of%20non-invasive%20precancer%20that%2C%20if%20left%20untreated%2C%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20turn%20into%20invasive%20cancer%2C%20although%20the%20chances%20are%20low.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20quite%20possible%20that%20just%20removing%20that%20lump%20all%20by%20itself%20could%20have%20been%20sufficient%20treatment%2C%26quot%3B%20Pyke%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMacpherson%20also%20said%20she%20had%20a%20previous%20cancer%20scare%20in%202014%20when%20a%20lump%20she%20found%20in%20her%20breast%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20benign%20cyst.%20It%20prompted%20her%20to%20seek%20out%20a%20naturopath%2C%20a%20type%20of%20alternative-medicine%20practitioner%2C%20and%20to%20found%20her%20wellness%20brand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDr.%20Liz%20O'Riordan%2C%20a%20breast%20cancer%20surgeon%20and%20advocate%20for%20breast%20cancer%20awareness%2C%20wrote%20on%20X%20in%20response%20to%20the%20interview%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20potential%20dangers%20of%20choosing%20alternative%20treatment%20for%20breast%20cancer%20can%20increase%20your%20risk%20of%20dying%20by%20six%20times.%20There%20is%20no%20evidence%20to%20prove%20that%20any%20of%20it%20works.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EO'Riordan%20didn't%20provide%20a%20source%20for%20the%20statistic%2C%20but%20a%202017%20study%20published%20in%20the%20Journal%20of%20the%20National%20Cancer%20Institute%20found%20that%20patients%20with%20breast%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcolorectal-cancer-high-mortality-young-people-signs-symptoms-disease-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecolorectal%20cancer%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20had%20alternative%20therapies%20as%20their%20initial%20treatment%20were%20five%20times%20more%20likely%20to%20die%20after%20five%20years%20than%20those%20who%20chose%20conventional%20medicine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'd%20urge%20women%20not%20to%20assume%20that%20because%20it's%20worked%20for%20her%20so%20far%2C%20it%20will%20work%20for%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20O'Riordan%20wrote%20in%20another%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20also%20some%20confusion%20over%20the%20exact%20meaning%20of%20%26quot%3Bintraductal%2C%26quot%3B%20O'Riordan%20noted%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FLiz_ORiordan%2Fstatus%2F1831268410858123419%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eon%20X%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20it%20could%20refer%20to%20%26quot%3Bductal%20carcinoma%20in%20situ%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20precancerous%20form%20of%20breast%20cancer%20that%20can't%20spread%20and%20therefore%20wouldn't%20warrant%20chemotherapy.%20Or%20%26quot%3Binvasive%20ductal%20cancer%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20invasive%20form%2C%20which%20is%20often%20treated%20with%20chemotherapy%20to%20prevent%20recurrence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWithout%20Elle%20making%20a%20comment%20or%20her%20surgeon%20commenting%20to%20explain%20exactly%20what%20type%20of%20cancer%20she%20has%2C%20we%20don't%20really%20know%2C%26quot%3B%20O'Riordan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECeinwen%20Giles%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Shine%20Cancer%20Support%2C%20a%20charity%20that%20supports%20people%20who%20receive%20a%20cancer%20diagnosis%20in%20their%2020s%2C%2030s%2C%20and%2040s%20and%20who%20is%20also%20in%20remission%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20news%20reports%20not%20emphasizing%20that%20Macpherson%20had%20surgery%20could%20be%20harmful%20to%20vulnerable%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20stuff%20out%20there%2C%20particularly%20on%20the%20internet%2C%20that%20I%20think%20preys%20on%20vulnerable%20people%2C%20and%20I've%20been%20there%20myself%2C%20where%20you're%20desperately%20looking%20for%20something%20that%20will%20make%20you%20better%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20worry%20with%20that%20kind%20of%20thing%20is%20that%20people%20will%20see%20it%20and%20think%2C%20'oh%2C%20well%2C%20I'm%20not%20going%20to%20have%20any%20traditional%20treatments.%20I'm%20just%20going%20to%20go%20down%20a%20holistic%20route%20because%20it%20worked%20for%20her%2C'%26quot%3B%20Giles%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222775%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Elle%20Macpherson%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d86eaa14a5cd1fcc8d0e3a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222081%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMacpherson%20said%20she%20took%20a%20holistic%20approach%20to%20cancer%20treatment.%3Cp%3EGreg%20Allen%2FAP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22caa7e7aa-ef87-43cf-8f29-2965f7dc3732%5C%22%3EAlternative%20treatments%20are%20not%20backed%20by%20science%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMacpherson's%20holistic%20treatment%20involved%20renting%20a%20home%20in%20Arizona%20for%20eight%20months%2C%20where%20she%20was%20under%20the%20care%20of%20her%20primary%20doctor%2C%20who%20specializes%20in%20integrative%20medicine%2C%20an%20approach%20that%20uses%20both%20conventional%20and%20alternative%20therapies%2C%20as%20well%20as%20naturopath%2C%20holistic%20dentist%2C%20osteopath%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fare-chiropractors-doctors%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echiropractor%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20two%20therapists.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20told%20The%20Weekly%20that%20she%20devoted%20%26quot%3Bevery%20single%20minute%20to%20healing%20myself.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EComplementary%20therapies%2C%20such%20as%20yoga%2C%20therapy%2C%20and%20herbal%20medicine%2C%20are%20used%20by%20some%20people%20with%20cancer%20alongside%20medical%20treatment%20as%20they%20can%20help%20them%20cope%20with%20their%20symptoms%20better%2C%20the%20charity%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cancerresearchuk.org%2Fabout-cancer%2Ftreatment%2Fcomplementary-alternative-therapies%2Fabout%2Fdifference-between-therapies%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECancer%20Research%20UK%3C%2Fa%3E%20says%20on%20its%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20many%20reasons%20someone%20might%20want%20to%20try%20alternative%20therapies%2C%20the%20charity%20said%2C%20but%20there%20is%20no%20scientific%20or%20medical%20evidence%20to%20show%20that%20they%20can%20cure%20cancer.%20In%20fact%2C%20they%20might%20cause%20harmful%20side%20effects%20or%20interfere%20with%20medical%20treatment%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPatients%20are%20also%20not%20informed%20about%20the%20possible%20risks%2C%20survival%20rates%2C%20and%20side%20effects%20as%20they%20would%20be%20with%20conventional%20treatment.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20my%20worry%20with%20alternative%20medicine.%20People%20are%20being%20told%20that%20this%20will%20save%20their%20life%2C%20without%20being%20told%20about%20any%20of%20the%20side%20effects%2C%26quot%3B%20O'Riordan%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraph.co.uk%2Fhealth-fitness%2Fconditions%2Fcancer%2Fbreast-cancer-chemo-risks%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20modeling%20agency%20that%20represents%20Macpherson%20didn't%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20BI.%