usiness%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221ba31662-aa21-48fd-a0be-484ed5b7b8fc%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EChina%20fuels%20African%20growth%2C%20but%20not%20for%20free%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20decades%2C%20China's%20rulers%20built%20alliances%20with%20African%20nations%2C%20portraying%20them%20as%20engaged%20in%20a%20common%20struggle%20against%20the%20legacy%20of%20Western%20colonialism.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20China's%20economy%20grew%20at%20a%20ferocious%20pace%20from%20the%201990s%2C%20it%20engaged%20in%20extensive%20infrastructure%20projects%20in%20Africa%2C%20securing%20deals%20for%20lucrative%20minerals%20vital%20for%20its%20growing%20tech%20and%20renewable-energy%20sectors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202017%2C%20China%20opened%20its%20first%20overseas%20People's%20Liberation%20Army%20base%20in%20Djibouti%2C%20on%20the%20horn%20of%20Africa%2C%20adding%20a%20military%20dimension%20to%20its%20expansion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChina%20is%20now%20Africa's%20biggest%20trading%20partner%2C%20with%20bilateral%20trade%20reaching%20%24167.8%20billion%20in%20the%20first%20half%20of%20this%20year%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fchinaglobalsouth.com%2F2024%2F08%2F15%2Fchina-africa-trade-edges-higher-in-the-january-july-period%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChina's%20state%20media.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20its%20presence%20in%20Africa%20has%20also%20attracted%20criticism%2C%20with%20China's%20leaders%20accused%20of%20saddling%20African%20countries%20with%20vast%20debts%20in%20the%20form%20of%20loans%20to%20fund%20infrastructure%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%2C%20China's%20chief%20rival%20for%20overseas%20influence%20in%20Africa%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fg-20-summit-politics-covid-china-government-united-states-46a01f4190fae4ca260f0ab5beaa59a5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehas%20accused%20Beijing%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20seeking%20to%20exploit%20African%20countries%20and%20ensnare%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22270efc91-6046-4c91-bee6-d4eb073e0b7c%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESeeking%20Xi's%20favor%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20hasn't%20stopped%20African%20leaders%20from%20lining%20up%20to%20do%20business%20with%20China%2C%20even%20as%20they%20take%20on%20the%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20are%20likely%20to%20push%20this%20week%20for%20deals%20to%20lighten%20their%20debt%20burden%20and%20address%20concerns%20over%20global%20warming%2C%20said%20Wyne.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20leaders%20granted%20special%20one-to-one%20meetings%20with%20Xi%20are%20Cyril%20Ramaphosa%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fafrica.businessinsider.com%2Flocal%2Fmarkets%2Fafrican-leaders-likely-to-table-funding-dilemma-as-they-gather-in-china%2Ffszgr2e%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epresident%20of%20South%20Africa%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20William%20Ruto%2C%20the%20president%20of%20Kenya.%20The%20economies%20are%20among%20Africa's%20biggest%2C%20though%20Kenya%20has%2C%20in%20recent%20months%2C%20been%20rocked%20by%20riots%20over%20economic%20instability%20caused%20by%20its%20debts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChina's%20economic%20downturn%20and%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20saw%20its%20investment%20in%20Africa%20dip%20sharply.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20data%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bu.edu%2Fgdp%2Ftag%2Fchinese-loans-to-africa%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBoston%20University's%20Global%20Development%20Policy%20Center%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20China's%20loans%20to%20Africa%20rose%20to%20%244.6%20billion%20in%202023%2C%20an%20increase%20from%20the%20%241%20billion%20loaned%20in%202022%2C%20but%20a%20massive%20reduction%20of%20the%20nearly%20%2430%20billion%20in%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20the%20major%20projects%20it%20pitched%20around%20a%20decade%20ago%2C%20China%20will%20likely%20propose%20smaller%20deals%20to%20African%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGiven%20the%20concerns%20of%20some%20African%20countries%20over%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20Belt%20and%20Road%20Initiative%20on%20their%20indebtedness%20and%20environments%2C%20China%20will%20seek%20to%20pitch%20smaller%2C%20more%20sustainable%20investments%20across%20the%20continent%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Wyne.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e1da025b-79be-4f13-860d-4a1414905ac2%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EChina%20portrays%20itself%20as%20leader%20of%20the%20'Global%20South'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfrica%20remains%20vital%20to%20China's%20strategy%20of%20portraying%20itself%20as%20the%20champion%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bglobal%20south%26quot%3B%20of%20non-Western%20nations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETensions%20between%20China%20and%20the%20West%20have%20increased%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20Ukraine%20war%2C%20in%20which%20China%20has%20provided%20support%20to%20Russia.%20And%20leaders%20in%20Western%20countries%20are%20increasingly%20alarmed%20by%20China's%20growing%20global%20assertiveness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20conference%20this%20week%20presents%20China%20with%20an%20opportunity%20to%20present%20itself%20as%20a%20global%20power%20broker.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%5BChina%5D%20will%20also%20aim%20to%20demonstrate%20that%2C%20even%20as%20advanced%20industrial%20democracies%20increasingly%20align%20to%20contest%20its%20influence%2C%20it%20is%20far%20from%20diplomatically%20isolated%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20developing%20world.%20In%26quot%3B%20said%20Wyne.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-showcases-global-power-with-africa-summit-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725459358000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d8441a289b805d1db3ebf3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-showcases-global-power-with-africa-summit-2024-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22China%20influence%20in%20Africa's%20growing%20amid%20its%20intensifying%20global%20rivalry%20with