of%20the%20idea%20of%20India%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20PTI%2C%20Mr%20Pitroda%20also%20asserted%20that%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20all%20the%20qualities%20of%20a%20future%20prime%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Pitroda%2C%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20Indian%20Overseas%20Congress%2C%20dismissed%20as%20%26quot%3Bbogus%26quot%3B%20the%20BJP's%20attack%20on%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20in%20the%20past%20over%20his%20remarks%20critical%20of%20the%20government%20during%20his%20visits%20abroad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20Mr%20Gandhi's%20upcoming%20visit%20to%20the%20US%20next%20week%2C%20Mr%20Pitroda%20said%20he%20is%20not%20coming%20to%20the%20US%20in%20his%20official%20capacity%20but%20will%20have%20a%20chance%20to%20interact%20with%20a%20variety%20of%20people%20on%20Capitol%20Hill%20at%20an%20%26quot%3Bindividual%20level%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20(Gandhi)%20will%20definitely%20have%20interactions%20with%20the%20press%20at%20the%20national%20press%20club%2C%20he%20will%20meet%20with%20the%20think%20tank%20people%20and%20will%20also%20have%20interaction%20at%20Georgetown%20University%20which%20is%20equally%20important%20in%20Washington%20DC%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Indian%20Overseas%20Congress%20chief%20said%20of%20Gandhi's%20first%20visit%20to%20the%20US%20since%20assuming%20the%20mantle%20of%20the%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20Gandhi%20will%20visit%20the%20US%20from%20September%208-10%20during%20which%20he%20will%20hold%20numerous%20interactions%20in%20Washington%20DC%20and%20Dallas%2C%20including%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Georgetown%20and%20the%20University%20of%20Texas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20similarities%20and%20divergences%20between%20former%20prime%20minister%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20and%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20Pitroda%20said%20he%20had%20worked%20with%20a%20number%20of%20prime%20ministers%20closely%20such%20as%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%2C%20PV%20Narasimha%20Rao%2C%20Manmohan%20Singh%2C%20VP%20Singh%2C%20Chandra%20Sekhar%20and%20HD%20Deve%20Gowda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20an%20opportunity%20to%20see%20many%20prime%20ministers%20from%20very%20close%20quarters%20but%20the%20difference%20between%20Rahul%20and%20Rajiv%20maybe%20is%20that%20Rahul%20is%20much%20more%20intellectual%2C%20thinker%2C%20Rajiv%20was%20a%20little%20more%20doer.%20They%20have%20the%20same%20DNA%2C%20they%20have%20the%20same%20concerns%20and%20feelings%20for%20the%20people%2C%20they%20genuinely%20believe%20in%20building%20a%20better%20India%20for%20everybody%2C%20they%20are%20genuinely%20simple%20people.%20They%20don't%20have%20big%20personal%20needs%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Congress%20leader%20told%20PTI%20from%20Chicago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRahul%20is%20a%20strategist%20more%20so%20than%20Rajiv%20was.%20They%20are%20products%20of%20different%20times%2C%20different%20tools%2C%20and%20different%20experiences.%20Poor%20Rahul%20has%20gone%20through%20two%20big%20shocks%20in%20life%2C%20(death%20of)%20his%20grandmother%20and%20his%20father.%20So%20they%20have%20had%20different%20paths%20to%20travel%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20fundamentals%20are%20clear%2C%20both%20are%20%26quot%3Bcustodians%20of%20the%20idea%20of%20India%26quot%3B%20that%20the%20Congress%20party%20had%20laid%20out%20and%20every%20leader%20of%20the%20party%20believed%20in%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNarasimha%20Rao%20believed%20in%20it%2C%20(Mallikarjun)%20Kharge%20ji%20believes%20in%20it%20and%20collectively%20it%20is%20our%20job%20to%20build%20the%20India%20our%20founding%20fathers%20had%20envisaged%2C%26quot%3B%20Pitroda%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20image%20is%20finally%20coming%20through%20the%20way%20he%20is%20and%20the%20two%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatras%20had%20helped%20in%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFirst%20of%20all%2C%20the%20image%20created%20in%20the%20media%20was%20based%20on%20a%20well-orchestrated%20campaign%20against%20an%20individual%20where%20millions%20and%20millions%20of%20dollars%20were%20spent%20on%20maligning%20this%20young%20man%20and%20when%20he%20is%20highly%20educated%2C%20people%20said%20he%20never%20went%20to%20college.%20People%20created%20this%20image%20by%20spending%20a%20lot%20of%20money.%20It%20was%20a%20false%20image.%20I%20give%20a%20lot%20of%20credit%20to%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20for%20standing%20up%20and%20fighting%20it%20for%20a%20long%20time%20and%20surviving%2C%20nobody%20else%20would%20have%20been%20able%20to%20survive%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Pitroda%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20onslaught%20day%20in%20and%20day%20out%20on%20an%20individual%2C%20his%20family%2C%20his%20legacy%2C%20his%20party%20character%2C%20it%20is%20bad.%20These%20are%20mean%20people%20who%20by%20design%20lie%2C%20cheat%20and%20say%20all%20kinds%20of%20things%20about%20individuals.%20I%20have%20seen%20that%20in%20my%20case%20also%20to%20a%20very%20small%20extent%2C%26quot%3B%20the%2082-year-old%20technocrat%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPitroda%20said%20things%20have%20turned%20around%20in%20the%20public's%20mind%20because%20they%20are%20beginning%20to%20realise%20that%20the%20media%20is%20controlled%2C%20messages%20are%20designed%20to%20hurt%20people%20and%20lies%20are%20finally%20catching%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20cannot%20lie%20all%20the%20time%20to%20the%20people.%20People%20are%20now%20beginning%20to%20see%20that%20it%20was%20said%20'we%20will%20create%2020%20million%20jobs'%2C%20but%20they%20haven't%20done%20that%2C%20it%20was%20said%20black%20money%20will%20be%20brought%20back%2C%20it%20hasn't%20happened%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20whether%20he%20sees%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20as%20a%20future%20PM%2C%20Pitroda%20said%20that%20is%20for%20the%20people%20to%20decide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrom%20my%20personal%20experience%20and%20I%20may%20be%20biased%2C%20I%20think%20he%20is%20very%20capable.%20He%20is%20a%20decent%20human%20being%2C%20he%20is%20well%20educated%2C%20he%20has%20the%20right%20DNA%20and%20I%20see%20him%20as%20the%20custodian%20of%20the%20idea%20of%20democracy%20that%20the%20Congress%20has%20always%20promoted%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20Congress%20leaders'%20view%20that%20Gandhi%20had%20earned%20the%20right%20to%20assume%20the%20post%20of%20PM%20when%20the%20Congress%20comes%20to%20power%2C%20Pitroda%20said%20he%20agrees%20with%20the%20view%20but%20ultimately%20it%20is%20for%20the%20party%20to%20decide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20whether%20he%20sees%20qualities%20of%20a%20future%20PM%20in%20Mr%20Gandhi%2C%20Mr%20Pitroda%20emphatically%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAbsolutely%2C%20no%20question%20about%20it.%26quot%3B%20Asked%20about%20the%20attack%20his%20party%20and%20he%20faced%20from%20the%20BJP%20during%20the%20past%20foreign%20visits%20of%20Gandhi%20over%20his%20critical%20remarks%2C%20Pitroda%20said%20that%20in%20this%20day%20and%20age%20when%20communication%20is%20instant%20and%20distance%20is%20dead%2C%20there%20are%20no%20local%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20local%20event%20becomes%20a%20global%20event%2C%20a%20church%20burn%20in%20France%20is%20no%20longer%20a%20French%20event%2C%20it%20is%20a%20global%20event%20as%20an%20example.%20Same%20with%20wars.%20So%20it%20is%20wrong%20to%20assume%20that%20there%20are%20certain%20things%20you%20say%20at%20home%20and%20there%20are%20certain%20things%20you%20say%20abroad%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCriticising%20the%20government%20is%20not%20criticising%20India.%20It%20is%20ok%20to%20criticise%20the%20government%20by%20an%20opposition%20leader%2C%20That%20is%20his%20job%20in%20fact%2C%20so%20why%20complain%3F%20I%20think%20this%20whole%20business%20of%20criticising%20abroad%20is%20bogus%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Indian%20Overseas%20Congress%20chairman%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20June%204%20Lok%20Sabha%20poll%20results%20and%20its%20significance%2C%20Pitroda%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIn%20the%20last%20election%20the%20fear%20was%20that%20the%20BJP%20will%20get%20400%20seats.%20Then%20it%20would%20have%20been%20an%20absolute%20majority%20which%20could%20bring%20about%20in%20the%20judgement%20of%20many%20people%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20concern%20at%20various%20levels%20on%20the%20Constitution%2C%20authoritarian%20mindset%20and%20more%20attack%20on%20the%20opposition%20and%20media.%20So%20this%20election%20was%20very%20important%20because%20the%20BJP%20could%20be%20brought%20down%20to%20240%20seats.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20message%20is%20loud%20and%20clear%20that%20ordinary%20people%20of%20India%20prefer%20democracy%2C%20Constitution%2C%20freedom%20and%20justice%2C%20he%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725457860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fj5sq8d3o_rahul-gandhi-sam-pitroda_625x300_04_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frahul-more-intellectual-strategist-compared-with-rajiv-gandhi-sam-pitroda-6490333%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rahul%20Gandhi%20is%20more%20intellectual%20and%20more%20of%20a%20strategist%20as%20compared%20with%20his%20father%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%2C%20says%20long-time%20Gandhi%20family%20confidant%20Sam%20Pitroda%2C%20describing%20both%20leaders%20as%20%26quot%3Bcustodians%20of%20the%20idea%20of%20India%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frahul-more-intellectual-strategist-compared-with-rajiv-gandhi-sam-pitroda-6490333%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Stock%20marke