tech%20veteran%20Ari%20Paparo%2C%20CEO%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.marketecture.tv%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMarketecture%20Media%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20producing%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmonopoly.marketecture.tv%2F%3Futm_source%3Dmonopoly.marketecture.tv%26utm_medium%3Dnewsletter%26utm_campaign%3Dscoop-we-found-the-deck-doubleclick-used-to-sell-itself-to-google%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Monopoly%20Report%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20newsletter%20to%20accompany%20Google's%20adtech%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPaparo%20confirmed%20the%20document's%20authenticity%20with%20two%20people%20with%20direct%20knowledge%20of%20the%20matter.%20(Paparo%20was%20a%20DoubleClick%20employee%20when%20the%20document%20was%20produced%20but%20didn't%20have%20access%20to%20it%20at%20the%20time.)%20Business%20Insider%20has%20separately%20confirmed%20the%20document's%20authenticity%20with%20a%20person%20with%20direct%20knowledge.%20This%20person%20was%20granted%20anonymity%20amid%20the%20high-profile%20and%20active%20litigation.%20Business%20Insider%20could%20not%20confirm%20with%20certainty%20whether%20this%20was%20a%20final%20draft.%20Five%20slides%20from%20a%20later%20version%20of%20the%20deck%20are%20also%20included%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.courtlistener.com%2Frecap%2Fgov.uscourts.vaed.533508%2Fgov.uscourts.vaed.533508.1194.18.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etrial's%20exhibits%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20submitted%20by%20the%20plaintiffs%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDoubleClick%20was%20pitching%20itself%20to%20potential%20suitors%20Yahoo%2C%20Microsoft%2C%20AOL%2C%20and%20Google%20%E2%80%94%20hence%20references%20to%20%26quot%3BYMAG%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20deck%20%E2%80%94%20all%20of%20which%20submitted%20bids%20for%20the%20company%2C%20according%20to%20a%20person%20with%20direct%20knowledge.%20Google%20won%20out%2C%20paying%20%243.1%20billion%20in%20a%202007%20deal%20that%20officially%20closed%20in%20March%202008.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Department%20of%20Justice%20and%2017%20states%20claim%20in%20their%20complaint%20that%20Google%20reached%20dominance%20in%20the%20%24300%20billion%20adtech%20and%20throttled%20competition%20by%20making%20key%20acquisitions%20and%20manipulating%20ad%20prices.%20The%20DOJ%20and%20the%20states%20are%20seeking%20a%20breakup%20of%20Google's%20adtech%20business%2C%20which%20could%20have%20big%20ramifications%20on%20the%20broader%20digital%20ad%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20concerns%20the%20under-the-hood%20part%20of%20Google's%20advertising%20business%3A%20The%20technology%20that%20connects%20advertisers%20with%20publishers%20and%20that%20runs%20the%20advertising%20auctions%20that%20take%20place%20in%20the%20milliseconds%20it%20takes%20a%20webpage%20to%20load.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20didn't%20provide%20a%20comment%20for%20this%20story.%20%26quot%3BWe%20look%20forward%20to%20setting%20the%20record%20straight%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Ftechnology%2Fgoogle-loses-bid-end-us-antitrust-case-over-digital-advertising-2024-06-14%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20company%20told%20Reuters%20in%20June%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20when%20a%20judge%20ruled%20the%20case%20would%20go%20to%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExcerpts%20from%20the%2049-slide%20pitch%20deck%20below%20outline%20how%20DoubleClick%20was%20positioning%20itself%20as%20a%20key%20asset%20to%20help%20a%20potential%20Big%20Tech%20acquirer%20become%20an%20advertising%20giant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBI%20has%20analyzed%20how%20the%202007%20document%20could%20become%20a%20central%20part%20of%20next%20week's%20blockbuster%20trial%2C%20which%20is%20set%20to%20begin%20on%20September%209.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EDoubleClick%20was%20pitching%20its%20business%20to%20the%20biggest%20players%20in%20adtech%20at%20the%20time%3A%20Yahoo%2C%20Microsoft%2C%20AOL%2C%20and%20Google.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22DoubleClick%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d72fb71d8d2deb96b82e8f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Ari%20Paparo%2FMarketecture%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EDoubleClick%20was%20the%20largest%20publisher%20ad%20server%20%E2%80%94%20technology%20that%20helps%20publishers%20manage%20their%20ad%20inventory%20and%20decide%20which%20ads%20should%20appear.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22DoubleClick%20pitch%20deck%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d730a81d8d2deb96b82f69%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Ari%20Paparo%2FMarketecture%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20DOJ%20claims%20in%20its%20suit%20that%20DoubleClick's%20ad%20server%20had%20a%20roughly%2060%25%20market%20share%20at%20the%20time.%20It%20also%20owned%20a%20relatively%20new%20ad%20exchange%20called%20AdX%20that%20helped%20connect%20ad%20buyers%20and%20publishers%20in%20online%20ad%20auctions.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20a%20slide%20from%20the%20DOJ%E2%80%99s%20complaint%20that%20maps%20out%20Google%E2%80%99s%20entire%20adtech%20business%20as%20of%20last%20year.%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221276%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Google's%20ad%20tech%20stack%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d73157289b805d1db399e2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22666%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Department%20of%20Justice%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPost-acquisition%2C%20the%20DoubleClick%20assets%20later%20became%20Google%20Ad%20Manager%2C%20which%20the%20DOJ%20claims%20in%20its%20complaint%20has%20a%20roughly%2090%25%20share%20of%20the%20US%20publisher%20ad%20server%20market.%20The%20Google%20AdExchange%20grew%20to%20around%20a%2050%25%20market%20share%2C%20the%20DOJ%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Federal%20Trade%20Commission%20approved%20the%20Google-DoubleClick%20acquisition%20in%202007%20after%20an%20eight-month%20investigation.%20The%20agency%20concluded%20that%20competition%20at%20the%20time%20among%20firms%20in%20the%20market%20was%20%26quot%3Bvigorous%2C%20and%20will%20likely%20increase.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20entire%20DoubleClick%20business%20was%20projected%20to%20generate%20%24323.6%20million%20in%20revenue%20by%20the%20end%20of%202007.%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22DoubleClick%20pitch%20deck%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d731fc14a5cd1fcc8cad01%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Ari%20Paparo%2FMarketecture%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EDoubleClick%20worked%20with%20advertisers%2C%20too.%20It%20positioned%20its%20offering%20as%20DART%2C%20which%20stands%20for%20Dynamic%20Advertising%2C%20Reporting%2C%20and%20Targeting.%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22DoubleClick%20pitch%20deck%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d7323c289b805d1db39b8f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Ari%20Paparo%2FMarketecture%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20DOJ's%20suit%20hinges%20on%20how%20through%20acquisitions%2C%20Google%20came%20to%20dominate%20both%20the%20publisher%20and%20advertiser%20side%20of%20the%20adtech%20stack%20%E2%80%94%20as%20well%20as%20the%20auction%20that%20takes%20place%20between%20them%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that%20it%20used%20that%20position%20to%20lock%20in%20its%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGoogle%20feared%20that%20if%20a%20rival%20acquired%20DoubleClick%2C%20Google%20would%20not%20control%20all%20the%20tools%20that%20link%20Google's%20advertisers%20with%20publisher%20inventory%3B%20in%20short%2C%20a%20rival%20could%20'disintermediate'%20Google%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20DOJ%20says%20in%20its%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20key%20phrase%20to%20look%20out%20for%20in%20this%20slide%20is%20'dynamic%20allocation.'%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22DoubleClick%20pitch%20deck%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d7329114a5cd1fcc8cadc0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Ari%20Papro%2FMarketecture%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20phrase%20%26quot%3Bdynamic%20allocation%26quot%3B%20appears%2055%20times%20in%20the%20DOJ's%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20refers%20to%20an%20auction%20mechanism%20where%2C%20the%20DOJ%20says%2C%20Google%20could%20configure%20its%20ad%20server%20to%20give%20its%20AdX%20ad%20exchange%20the%20first%20chance%20to%20buy%20a%20publisher's%20ad%20inventory%20before%20it%20was%20offered%20out%20to%20rival%20ad%20exchanges%20%E2%80%94%20and%20at%20lower%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EDoubleClick%20outlines%20that%20a%20competitive%20advantage%20was%20that%20its%20advertiser%20clients%20could%20'cherry-pick'%20the%20best%20ad%20inventory.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22DoubleClick%20pitch%20deck%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d73343289b805d1db39cf2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Ari%20Paparo%2FMarketecture%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDoubleClick%20owns%20the%20primary%20ad%20management%20platform%20%E2%80%94%20enables%20dynamic%20allocation%20across%20direct%20and%20indirect%20channels%20and%20advanced%20targeting%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20DoubleClick%20sales%20pitch%20reads.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20DOJ%20says%20in%20the%20suit%20that%20Google%20programmed%20its%20ad%20server%20to%20prevent%20publishers%20from%20offering%20better%20terms%20to%20other%20ad%20exchanges%20beyond%20AdX.%20Dynamic%20allocation%2C%20the%20suit%20alleges%2C%20%26quot%3Bpredictably%20reinforced%20publishers'%20dependence%20on%20both%20AdX%20and%20DFP.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EDoubleClick%20outlines%20the%20revenue%20opportunity%20for%20its%20eventual%20buyer%20as%20'a%20race%20to%20the%20finish%20line.'%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22DoubleClick%20pitch%20deck%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d733891d8d2deb96b83217%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Ari%20Paparo%2FMarketecture%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20end%2C%20the%20winner%20will%20be%20the%20company%20with%20the%20largest%20pool%20of%20liquidity%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20slide%20reads.%20DoubleClick%20said%20the%20winner%20would%20achieve%20this%20by%20becoming%20the%20go-to%20ad%20server%2C%20by%20allowing%20for%20an%20open%20flow%20of%20ad%20inventory%20and%20data%2C%20and%20offering%20solutions%20for%20all%20types%20of%20different%20inventory.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EFor%20Yahoo%2C%20which%20this%20particular%20deck%20was%20aimed%20at%2C%20the%20'total%20estimated%20annual%20revenue%20opportunity'%20was%20%242.6%20billion%20after%20the%20company%20had%20paid%20relevant%20traffic%20acquisition%20costs.%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22DoubleClick%20pitch%20deck%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d733b7289b805d1db39d30%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Ari%20Paparo%2FMarketecture%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20Google's%20Ad%20Manager%2C%20AdSense%20for%20Content%2C%20and%20DV360%20adtech%20businesses%20generated%20%2415%20billion%20in%20gross%20revenue%20and%20%242.9%20billion%20in%20net%20revenue%2C%20according%20to%20the%20published%20trial%20exhibits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndustry%20analyst%20Brian%20Wieser%2C%20principal%20at%20Madison%20and%20Wall%2C%20estimated%20that%20Google%20had%20a%20nearly%2050%25%20share%20of%20the%20US%20ad%20server%20and%20exchange%20adtech%20market%20and%20around%20a%20third%20of%20the%20demand-side%20platform%2C%20or%20advertiser%2C%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fleaked-deck-doubleclick-acquisition-pitch-google-adtech-antitrust-trial-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725453010000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d72fb71d8d2deb96b82e8f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fleaked-deck-doubleclick-acquisition-pitch-google-adtech-antitrust-trial-2024-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20pitch%20deck%20shows%20how%20DoubleClick%20was%20positioning%20itself%20as%20a%20key%20asset%20to%20help%20a%20potential%20Big%20Tech%20acquirer%20to%20become%20an%20advertising%20giant.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22loreilly%40insider.com%20(Lara%20O'Reilly)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A24%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fleaked-deck-doubleclick-acquisition-pitch-google-adtech-antitrust-trial-2024-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22No%20pension%20for%20defected%20MLAs%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20as%20assembly%20passes%20new%20bill%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725452988000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-113064033%2Cimgsize-748970.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fno-pension-for-defected-mlas-in-himachal-pradesh-as-assembly-passes-new-bill%2Farticleshow%2F113063692.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20government%2C%20under%20CM%20Sukhvinder%20Singh%20Sukhu%2C%20has%20approved%20a%20bill%20revoking%20pension%20benefits%20for%20state%20legislators%20disqualified%20under%20the%20anti-defection%20law.%20This%20legislative%20move%20aims%20to%20deter%20defection%20and%20preserve%20democratic%20values.%20Recently%2C%20six%20Congress%20MLAs%20were%20disqualified%20for%20cross-voting%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20temporarily%20reducing%20the%20party's%20strength.%20%E2%80%8B%E2%80%8BThe%20Congress%20government%20in%20the%20state%20had%20to%20grapple%20with%20a%20crisis%20as%20its%20strength%20had%20reduced%20to%2034%20legislators.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fno-pension-for-defected-mlas-in-himachal-pradesh-as-assembly-passes-new-bill%2Farticleshow%2F113063692.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Kicked%20in%20spine'%3A%20Indian%20grandfather%20tragically%20beaten%20to%20death%20by%20children%20in%20UK%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725452738000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-113065686%2Cimgsize-69356.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fkicked-him-in-spine-how-indian-grandfather-bhim-sen-kohli-was-tragically-beaten-to-death-by-children-in-leicester%2Farticleshow%2F113065289.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sources%20also%20claim%20that%20the%20group%20of%20young%20people%20suspected%20to%20be%20responsible%20for%20the%20horrifying%20tragedy%20fled%20the%20scene%20after%20brutally%20assaulting%20him.%20The%20victim%20was%20left%20screaming%20in%20agony%20at%20the%20scene%2C%20his%20daughter%20said%2C%20according%20to%20The%20Sun.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20WORLD%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fkicked-him-in-spine-how-indian-grandfather-bhim-sen-kohli-was-tragically-beaten-to-death-by-children-in-leicester%2Farticleshow%2F113065289.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BCan%20We%20Be%20So%20Rigid%3F%26quot%3B%20Supreme%20Court%20Grills%20Central%20Agency%20In%20Documents%20Case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20asked%20tough%20questions%20to%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%2C%20questioning%20if%20the%20agency's%20refusal%20to%20provide%20the%20accused%20with%20documents%20seized%20during%20a%20money%20laundering%20probe%20does%20not%20violate%20the%20fundamental%20right%20to%20life%20and%20personal%20liberty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20of%20Justice%20AS%20Oka%2C%20Justice%20A%20Amanullah%20and%20Justice%20AG%20Masih%20was%20hearing%20an%20appeal%20related%20to%20the%20supply%20of%20documents%20in%20a%20money%20laundering%20case.%20The%202022%20Sarla%20Gupta%20vs%20ED%20case%20pertains%20to%20the%20question%20on%C2%A0whether%20the%20investigating%20agency%20can%20deprive%20the%20accused%20of%20crucial%20documents%20it%20is%20relying%20on%20in%20a%20PMLA%20case%20in%20the%20pre-trial%20stage.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%20(PMLA)%20has%20come%20under%20the%20spotlight%20in%20several%20high-profile%20cases%20after%20top%20politicians%2C%20including%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20his%20Jharkhand%20counterpart%20Hemant%20Soren%2C%20AAP%20leader%20Manish%20Sisodia%20and%20BRS%20leader%20K%20Kavitha%2C%20were%20arrested%20under%20this%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHearing%20the%20matter%2C%20the%20court%20asked%20if%20the%20accused%20can%20be%20denied%20the%20document%20solely%20on%20a%20technical%20ground.%20%26quot%3BWhy%20can't%20everything%20be%20transparent%3F%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Amanullah%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditional%20Solicitor%20General%20SV%20Raju%2C%20appearing%20for%20the%20ED%2C%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20the%20accused%20knows%20that%20there%20are%20documents%2C%20he%20can%20ask%2C%20but%20if%20he%20does%20not%20know%20and%20just%20has%20assumption%2C%20he%20cannot%20seek%20a%20roving%20enquiry%20on%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20then%20asked%20if%20this%20won't%20violate%20Article%2021%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20which%20guarantees%20right%20to%20life%20and%20liberty.%20%26quot%3BAlso%2C%20in%20a%20PMLA%20case%2C%20you%20may%20retrieve%20thousands%20of%20documents%20but%20you%20only%20rely%20on%2050%20of%20them.%20Accused%20may%20not%20remember%20every%20document.%20He%20may%20then%20ask%20that%20whatever%20document%20has%20been%20recovered%20from%20my%20place%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Oka%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20lawyer%20said%20the%20accused%20has%20a%20list%20of%20documents%20and%20cannot%20ask%20for%20them%20unless%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Bnecessary%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bdesirable%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20modern%20times%2C%20suppose%20he%20applies%20for%20documents%20running%20into%20thousands%20of%20pages.%20This%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20minutes%2C%20can%20easily%20be%20scanned%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Oka%20noted%20that%20%26quot%3Btimes%20are%20changing%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BBoth%20us%20and%20advocates%20on%20the%20other%20side%2C%20we%20have%20objective%20to%20do%20justice.%20Are%20we%20going%20to%20be%20so%20rigid%20that%20the%20person%20is%20facing%20prosecution%20but%20we%20go%20and%20say%20that%20the%20documents%20are%20protected%3F%20Will%20this%20be%20justice%3F%20There%20are%20cases%20so%20heinous%20where%20bail%20is%20given%2C%20but%20nowadays%20people%20are%20not%20getting%20bail%20in%20Magistrate%20cases.%20Times%20are%20changing.%20Can%20we%20as%20this%20bench%20be%20so%20rigid%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20said%20an%20accused%20has%20the%20right%20to%20seek%20documents%20if%20he%2Fshe%20relies%20on%20them%20to%20seek%20bail%20or%20dismissal%20of%20the%20case.%20Mr%20Raju%20contested%20this.%20%26quot%3BNo%20there%20is%20no%20right%20as%20such...%20He%20can%20request%20the%20court%20to%20look%20into%20this.%20Suppose%20there%20is%20no%20document%20as%20such%20and%20is%20a%20clear%20case%20of%20conviction%20and%20he%20only%20wants%20to%20delay%20the%20trial%2C%20it%20cannot%20be%20a%20right.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20has%20reserved%20the%20judgment%20in%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PMLA%20has%20repeatedly%20come%20under%20the%20lens%20after%20several%20high-profile%20Opposition%20leaders%20were%20arrested%20by%20central%20agencies%20under%20the%20anti-corruption%20law.%20While%20granting%20bail%20to%20Prem%20Prakash%2C%20allegedly%20an%20aide%20of%20Jharkhand%20Chief%20Minister%20Hemant%20Soren%2C%20in%20a%20money%20laundering%20case%20last%20month%2C%20the%20court%20noted%2C%20%26quot%3BRelying%20on%20the%20judgment%20in%20Manish%20Sisodia%2C%20we%20have%20said%20that%20even%20in%20PMLA%20(Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act)%2C%20bail%20is%20a%20rule%20and%20jail%20the%20exception.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20referred%20to%20Section%2045%20of%20the%20PMLA%20that%20mentions%20twin%20conditions%20for%20bail%20--%20there%20should%20be%20prima%20facie%20satisfaction%20that%20the%20accused%20has%20not%20committed%20the%20offence%20and%20that%20he%20is%20not%20likely%20to%20commit%20any%20offence%20while%20on%20bail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20that%20Section%2045%20specifies%2C%20the%20court%20said%2C%20is%20that%20the%20conditions%20must%20be%20met%20for%20bail.%20%26quot%3BLiberty%20of%20the%20individual%20is%20always%20the%20rule%20and%20deprivation%2C%20by%20procedure%20established%20by%20law%2C%20the%20exception.%20Twin%20test%20does%20not%20take%20away%20this%20principle%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725452700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F4qgfvaco_supreme-court-new_625x300_11_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-enforcement-directorate-can-we-be-so-rigid-top-court-grills-central-agency-in-documents-case-6489135%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20asked%20tough%20questions%20to%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%2C%20questioning%20if%20the%20agency's%20refusal%20to%20provide%20the%20accused%20with%20documents%20seized%20during%20a%20money%20laundering%20probe%20does%20not%20violate%20the%20right%20to%20liberty%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20beloved%20whale%20long%20suspected%20of%20being%20a%20Russian%20'spy'%20was%20shot%20dead%2C%20animal-rights%20groups%20say%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221718%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20white%20beluga%20whale%20in%20the%20water%2C%20wearing%20a%20harness.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5cc8759996a674085520dd42%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221145%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHvaldimir%2C%20a%20white%20beluga%20whale%2C%20wearing%20a%20harness%20off%20the%20Norwegian%20coast.%3Cp%3EReuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EHvaldimir%2C%20a%20beluga%20whale%20accused%20of%20being%20a%20Russian%20spy%2C%20was%20found%20dead%20off%20the%20coast%20of%20Norway.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAnimal-rights%20groups%20have%20filed%20a%20police%20report%20saying%20they%20believe%20the%20whale%20was%20shot%20to%20death.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20groups%20provided%20Business%20Insider%20with%20images%20that%20appeared%20to%20show%20bullet%20wounds%20on%20its%20body.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20white%20beluga%20whale%20nicknamed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbeluga-whale-spy-russia-found-dead-hvaldimir-norway-coast-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHvaldimir%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20beloved%20