-of-a-beluga-whale-playing-fetch-is-probably-not-what-it-seems%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplaying%20with%20a%20rugby%20ball%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20death%20of%20Hvaldimir%20came%20amid%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-demands-norway-pay-millions-for-reindeer-border-crossing-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrowing%20tensions%20between%20Russia%20and%20Norway%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20an%20active%20NATO%20member%20that%20has%20been%20ramping%20up%20military%20drills%20and%20exercises%20in%20the%20region%20because%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnordic-navies-focus-on-submarine-warfare-amid-tensions-with-russia-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efears%20of%20Russian%20aggression%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20injuries%20on%20the%20whale%20are%20alarming%20and%20of%20a%20nature%20that%20cannot%20rule%20out%20a%20criminal%20act%20%E2%80%94%20it%20is%20shocking%2C%26quot%3B%20Siri%20Martinsen%2C%20a%20veterinarian%20who's%20the%20leader%20of%20NOAH%2C%20said%20in%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BGiven%20the%20suspicion%20of%20a%20criminal%20act%2C%20it%20is%20crucial%20that%20the%20police%20are%20involved%20quickly.%20Hvaldimir%20was%20significant%20to%20many%2C%20and%20all%20facts%20must%20be%20brought%20to%20light%20regarding%20his%20death.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20conversation%20with%20BI%2C%20Martinsen%20said%20wasn't%20clear%20who%20might%20have%20shot%20Hvaldimir.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%2C%20we%20have%20no%20information%20about%20that%2C%20and%20that%20is%20why%20we%20are%20filing%20a%20report%20this%20early%20in%20the%20process%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMartinsen%20said%20that%20before%20the%20whale's%20death%2C%20her%20organization%20had%20assessed%20the%20risk%20level%20of%20Russia%20attempting%20to%20kill%20or%20capture%20the%20whale%20as%20%26quot%3Bextremely%20low.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3