in%20the%20Union%20Territory%20on%20Wednesday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20sees%20its%20first%20election%20in%20nearly%2010%20years%20as%20well%20as%20its%20first%20as%20a%20Union%20Territory%20after%20it%20was%20stripped%20of%20its%20special%20status%20under%20Article%20370%20in%202019%2C%20Mr%20Gandhi%20made%20the%20restoration%20of%20statehood%20the%20central%20plank%20of%20his%20addresses%20on%20Wednesday%20while%20also%20reminding%20people%20of%20the%20ties%20of%20blood%20he%20and%20his%20family%20share%20with%20them%2C%20going%20as%20far%20back%20as%20his%20great-grandfather%20and%20India's%20first%20Prime%20Minister%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20is%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20also%20took%20a%20jibe%20at%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20Manoj%20Sinha%20-%20and%20the%20BJP-led%20government%20at%20the%20Centre%20through%20him%20-%20by%20calling%20him%20a%20'%3Cem%3Eraja%3C%2Fem%3E'%20(king).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20which%20will%20see%20its%20campaign%20begin%20on%20Friday%20with%20rallies%20being%20addressed%20by%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20hit%20back%20and%20accused%20the%20Congress-National%20Conference%20alliance%20in%20the%20Union%20Territory%20of%20being%20supported%20by%20militants.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Kings%20Removed'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20rally%20for%20the%20Congress%20candidate%20from%20Dooru%2C%20Ghulam%20Ahmad%20Mir%2C%20with%20National%20Conference%20chief%20Farooq%20Abdullah%2C%20Mr%20Gandhi%20cited%20several%20decisions%20that%20had%20to%20be%20rolled%20back%20by%20the%20Centre%20and%20cited%20that%20as%20proof%20of%20the%20opposition%20INDIA%20alliance's%20growing%20strength%20in%20the%20country.%20This%20strength%2C%20he%20told%20his%20audience%2C%20would%20ensure%20that%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20would%20be%20granted%20statehood%20if%20the%20people%20voted%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20into%20power%20in%20the%20Union%20Territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%201947%2C%20we%20removed%20the%20kings%20and%20formed%20a%20democratic%20government.%20We%20gave%20the%20country%20a%20Constitution.%20But%20a%20%3Cem%3Eraja%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20ruling%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20today.%20His%20name%20is%20LG%20(lieutenant%20governor)%2C%20but%20he%20is%20a%20%3Cem%3Eraja%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Your%20money%20is%20being%20stolen%20and%20given%20to%20people%20from%20outside.%20Be%20that%20in%20the%20form%20of%20contracts%20or%20anything%20else...%20The%20first%20thing%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20done%20is%20restoring%20statehood%20to%20J%26amp%3BK%20because%20it%20wasn't%20just%20your%20state%20that%20was%20snatched...%20Your%20rights%2C%20your%20wealth%2C%20all%20of%20it%20is%20being%20snatched%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Gandhi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPersonal%20Relationship%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20another%20rally%20in%20Anantnag%2C%20he%20spoke%20about%20the%20personal%20ties%20he%20has%20with%20the%20people%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20know%20that%20you%20and%20I%20have%20a%20blood%20relation.%20This%20is%20not%20a%20political%20relationship.%20Be%20it%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%2C%20Indira%20Gandhi%20or%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%2C%20it%20is%20an%20old%20relationship.%20Whatever%20you%20want%20from%20me%2C%20my%20doors%20are%20always%20open%20for%20you.%20I%20want%20to%20serve%20you%20in%20Parliament.%20I%20will%20raise%20your%20issues%2C%20your%20pain%20and%20your%20sorrow.%20The%20country%20needs%20to%20know%20that%20this%20is%20the%20first%20time%20in%20India's%20history%20that%20a%20state%20has%20become%20a%20Union%20Territory%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gandhi%20also%20claimed%20that%20the%20BJP%20has%20used%20the%20Kashmiri%20Pandit%20issue%20for%20political%20reasons%20and%20has%20not%20helped%20the%20community.%20Using%20his%20oft-repeated%20'%3Cem%3Emohab