quot%3BI%20want%20to%20remind%20the%20people%20that%20the%20manifestoes%20released%20by%20the%20National%20Conference%2C%20PDP%20and%20others%20want%20to%20take%20J%26amp%3BK%20back%20to%20the%20old%20days%20and%20old%20problems.%20They%20are%20openly%20taking%20the%20support%20of%20militants%20to%20fight%20the%20elections.%20I%20am%20seeing%20that%20former%20militants%20are%20supporting%2C%20and%20campaigning%20for%2C%20National%20Conference%20and%20PDP%20candidates.%20We%20have%20to%20defeat%20such%20parties.%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20will%20see%20a%20government%20being%20formed%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJammu%20and%20Kashmir%20will%20vote%20in%20three%20phases%20between%20September%2018%20and%20October%201.%20Counting%20will%20take%20place%20on%20October%208.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725450540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fbkjqu2c_rahul-gandhi-kashmir_625x300_04_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjammu-and-kashmir-election-jammu-and-kashmir-rahul-gandhi-statehood-and-ties-of-blood-rahul-gandhis-election-pitch-in-j-k-6489191%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Aiming%20to%20win%20over%20the%20people%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20ahead%20of%20the%20Assembly%20elections%2C%20which%20begin%20in%20less%20than%20two%20weeks%2C%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20opted%20to%20mix%20a%20political%20pitch%20with%20an%20emotional%20one%20while%20kicking%20off%20his%20party's%20campaign%20in%20the%20UT%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjammu-and-kashmir-election-jammu-and-kashmir-rahul-gandhi-statehood-and-ties-of-blood-rahul-gandhis-election-pitch-in-j-k-6489191%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20moved%20from%20the%20US%20to%20Germany%202%20years%20ago.%20Here%20are%20the%207%20biggest%