%20with%20reach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20air-launched%20version%20of%20the%20Standard%20Missile%206%2C%20which%20is%20known%20as%20the%20AIM-174B%2C%20was%20spotted%20in%20photos%20by%20experts%20and%20analysts%20during%20its%20development%3B%20however%2C%20the%20details%20of%20the%20program%20were%20a%20bit%20unclear%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Navy%20acknowledged%20the%20AIM-174B%20in%20July%20when%20US%20Navy%20F%2FA-18E%20Super%20Hornets%20aboard%20the%20Nimitz-class%20aircraft%20carrier%20USS%20Carl%20Vinson%20and%20at%20Hawaii's%20Joint%20Base%20Pearl%20Harbor-Hickham%20were%20seen%20sporting%20the%20missiles%20during%20the%20Rim%20of%20the%20Pacific%20Exercise.%20The%20Navy%20revealed%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-navy-aircraft-spotted-sm6-missile-newly-tested-in-combat-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethis%20missile%20is%20now%20operational%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Experts%20then%20immediately%20assessed%20the%20focus%20was%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20AIM-174B%20is%20intended%20primarily%20for%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20to%20counter%20to%20developments%20within%20the%20People's%20Liberation%20Army%20Air%20Force%20(PLAAF)%20and%20naval%20aviation%2C%26quot%3B%20Douglas%20Barrie%2C%20a%20senior%20fellow%20for%20military%20aerospace%20at%20the%20International%20Institute%20for%20Strategic%20Studies%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.iiss.org%2Fonline-analysis%2Fmilitary-balance%2F2024%2F07%2Fphoenix-successor-redux-the-usns-range-riposte-to-chinas-pl-17%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrote%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20July.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplatform.twitter.com%2Fwidgets.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20SM-6%20Air%20Launched%20Configuration%20(ALC)%20