and-chinese-combat-air-trends-current-capabilities-and-future-threat-outlook%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20this%20missile%2C%20a%20follow-on%20to%20the%20PL-12%2C%20%26quot%3Bfeatures%20a%20miniature%20AESA%20seeker%20head%20and%20outranges%20the%20US-made%20AIM-120C%2FD%20AMRAAM%20series.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChina%20has%20also%20been%20working%20on%20longer-range%20options%2C%20like%20the%20PL-17%2C%20that%20are%20also%20pushing%20the%20US%20to%20develop%20new%20capabilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJustin%20Bronk%2C%20a%20RUSI%20airpower%20expert%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20%26quot%3BChina%20already%20deploys%20the%20PL-15%20missile%2C%20which%20has%20better%20kinematics%20than%20the%20AIM-120D3%2C%20so%20there%20is%20an%20incentive%26quot%3B%20to%20have%20a%20missile%20that%20%26quot%3Bcan%20match%20or%20exceed%20that%20performance.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224928%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20F%2FA-18E%20Super%20Hornet%20takes%20off%20on%20the%20deck%20of%20the%20Nimitz-class%20aircraft%20carrier%20USS%20Carl%20Vinson%20with%20the%20ocean%20in%20the%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d773ea289b805d1db3d673%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20F%2FA-18E%20Super%20Hornet%2C%20assigned%20to%20the%20%26quot%3BGolden%20Dragons%26quot%3B%20of%20Strike%20Fighter%20Squadron%20(VFA)%20192%2C%20launches%20from%20the%20flight%20deck%20of%20Nimitz-class%20aircraft%20carrier%20USS%20Carl%20Vinson%20(CVN%2070).%3Cp%3EU.S.%20Navy%20photo%20by%20Mass%20Communication%20Specialist%203rd%20Class%20Joshua%20Sapien%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20is%20even%20more%20important%2C%20he%20said%2C%20considering%20%26quot%3Bthe%20Super%20Hornet%20as%20the%20primary%20fighter%20type%20still%20for%20the%20US%20Navy%20has%20significantly%20less%20impressive%20kinematic%20performance%20itself%20than%20the%20J-20%20or%20J-16%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20carry%20the%20PL-15%20and%20PL-17.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20AIM-174B%20gives%20US%20Navy%20carrier%20air%20wings%20a%20new%20ability%20to%20engage%20China's%20air%20force%20and%20naval%20aviation%20aircraft%20at%20a%20greater%20range%20than%20its%20predecessor%2C%20potentially%20closing%20the%20gap.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ship-launched%20SM-6%20missile%2C%20also%20known%20as%20the%20RIM-174%2C%20is%20believed%20to%20have%20a%20range%20of%20up%20to%20230%20miles%2C%20and%20it%20saw%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-warships-used-weapon-combat-first-destroy-iranian-missiles-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecombat%20for%20the%20first%20time%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20fall%20against%20the%20Houthis.%20The%20missile%20is%20a%20three-in-one%20extended-range%20weapon%20for%20anti-air%20and%20anti-surface%20warfare.%20It's%20also%20able%20to%20kill%20ballistic%20missiles%20during%20the%20terminal%20phase%20of%20flight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20air-to-air%20role%2C%20it%20brings%20some%20of%20those%20capabilities%20to%20bear%20in%20new%20ways%20to%20help%20the%20US%20match%20newer%20Chinese%20weapons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBronk%20said%20the%20PL-17%20is%20probably%20most%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ecomparable%20to%20the%20AIM-174B%2C%20but%20the%20Chinese%20weapon%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Emight%20have%20a%20longer%20range%2C%20in%20part%20because%20of%20the%20platforms%20that%20are%20primarily%20going%20to%20be%20carrying%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223333%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Chinese%20fighter%20jet%20flies%20above%20with%20some%20decoy%20flares%20soaring%20behind%20it%20against%20a%20blue%20sky.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66ba51c1b4912df3ae1adf0c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221985%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20J-16%20fighter%20jet%20releases%20decoy%20flares%20during%20Changchun%20Air%20Show%20at%20Changchun%20Dafangshen%20Airport%20in%20Changchun%2C%20Jilin%20Province%20of%20China.%3Cp%3EZheng%20Shuai%2FVCG%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20PL-17%20is%20a%20rather%20large%20missile%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twz.com%2Fmassive-pl-17-air-to-air-missile-seen-on-chinese-j-16-fighters%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eappeared%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20Chinese%20J-16%20multirole%20strike%20fighter%20during%20development.%20More%20recently%2C%20amid%20indications%20it%20was%20approaching%20operational%20status%2C%20it%20was%20seen%20on%20the%20jet%20last%20December.%20China's%20J-16%20fighter%20jet%20is%20a%20highly%20capable%20fourth-generation%20aircraft.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20AIM-174B%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20is%20carried%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-navy-super-hornet-fighter-jets-arrive-middle-east-report-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENavy's%20Super%20Hornets%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Observers%20have%20noted%20that%20Super%20Hornets%20may%20have%20trouble%20carrying%20the%20AIM-174B%20due%20to%20its%20size%20and%20weight%20%E2%80%94%20the%20missile%20is%20likely%20five%20times%20the%20weight%20of%20the%20AIM-120D%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that%20the%20weapon%20could%20impact%20the%20jet's%20top%20speed%20and%20altitude.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20the%20new%20missile%20provides%20valuable%20reach.%20In%20an%20air%20combat%20scenario%20with%20China%2C%20the%20AIM-174B%20could%20likely%20be%20most%20useful%20at%20disrupting%20China's%20kill%20chain%2C%20or%20the%20process%20by%20which%20a%20target%20is%20identified%2C%20targeted%2C%20and%20destroyed%20and%20which%20assets%20are%20involved%20in%20completing%20that%20task.%20In%20particular%2C%20the%20missile%20could%20target%20China's%20airborne%20early%20warning%20and%20control%20aircraft%20that%20help%20set%20up%20those%20kill%20chains.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20gives%20American%20aircraft%20the%20ability%20to%20targ