-27-so-what-makes-september-4-special-for-the-company%2Farticleshow%2F113063601.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Google%20was%20incorporated%20on%20September%204%2C%201998%2C%20but%20celebrates%20its%20birthday%20on%20September%2027%20to%20commemorate%20a%20significant%20search%20indexing%20milestone.%20Founded%20by%20Larry%20Page%20and%20Sergey%20Brin%20in%20a%20Menlo%20Park%20garage%2C%20Google%20has%20evolved%20into%20a%20leading%20tech%20company%20with%20services%20like%20Gmail%20and%20Google%20Drive.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20TECH%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Fgoogle-celebrates-its-birthday-on-september-27-so-what-makes-september-4-special-for-the-company%2Farticleshow%2F113063601.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Bhopal%2C%20School%20Girls%20Destroy%20Fans%2C%20Windows%20To%20Protest%20Harsh%20Punishments%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EStudents%20at%20a%20government%20school%20for%20girls%20in%20Bhopal%20rose%20up%20in%20protest%20Wednesday%20claiming%20they%20are%20forced%20to%20clean%20the%20premises%20and%20classrooms%20and%20mow%20the%20lawn%2C%20and%20face%20harsh%20punishments%20for%20minor%20infractions%2C%20including%20standing%20in%20the%20baking%20sun%20if%20they%20are%20even%20five%20minutes%20late%20to%20class.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHundreds%20of%20girls%20from%20the%20Sarojini%20Naidu%20Girls%20Higher%20Secondary%20School%20took%20out%20a%20sit-in%20protest%20today%20against%20the%20management%20and%20an%20employee%20Varsha%20Jha%2C%20whom%20they%20have%20accused%20of%20mistreating%20them.%20Ms%20Jha%2C%20appointed%20only%20a%20month%20ago%2C%20has%20reportedly%20apologised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20school%20administration%20has%20refuted%20the%20students'%20claim%2C%20insisting%20teachers%20do%20not%20punish%20the%20students%20as%20alleged.%20The%20principal%2C%20Malini%20Verma%2C%20told%20NDTV%20an%20ex-soldier%20had%20been%20hired%20to%20enforce%20discipline.%20She%20also%20said%20senior%20Education%20Department%20officials%20would%20decide%20the%20next%20step.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVisuals%20from%20the%20school%20showed%20a%20horde%20of%20angry%20young%20girls%20in%20uniform%20gathered%20outside%20the%20school%20building%3B%20some%20are%20seen%20stomping%20furiously%20on%20a%20nameplate%20and%20others%20breaking%20windows.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20video%2C%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20a%20small%20crowd%20a%20handful%20of%20students%20are%20sitting%20on%20the%20ground%20-%20the%20sit-in%20protest%20team%20-%20using%20their%20hands%20to%20shield%20their%20faces%2C%20unsuccessfully%2C%20from%20the%20scorching%20sun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20third%20video%20shows%20the%20students%20sitting%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20sweating%20profusely%20under%20the%20midday%20sun%2C%20and%20shouting%20slogans%20against%20the%20school%20management%20and%20the%20teacher%2C%20Ms%20Jha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20fourth%20even%20showed%20some%20girls%20standing%20on%20classroom%20benches%20to%20pull%20down%20ceiling%20fans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20students%20were%20quoted%20by%20local%20media%20as%20also%20complaining%20about%20timings%3B%20school%20finishes%20at%206%20pm%2C%20they%20said%2C%20which%20makes%20it%20difficult%20for%20some%20girls%20who%20live%20far%20away.%20Another%20spoke%20of%20punishments%20that%20affected%20students'%20health%20and%20criticised%20teachers'%20for%20dismissing%20such%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20are%20late%20to%20school%2C%20even%20by%20a%20minute%2C%20we%20are%20sometimes%20not%20allowed%20inside...%20the%20gates%20are%20locked%20and%20we%20are%20punished%20by%20being%20made%20to%20stand%20in%20the%20heat%20for%20two%20hours.%20Many%20of%20us%20come%20from%20far%20away...%20it%20isn't%20our%20fault%20if%20we%20are%20late%20sometimes%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20student%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20flagged%20%26quot%3Ba%20new%20teacher%20who%20came%20to%20discipline%20students%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20scolds%20and%20punishes%20students%20who%20make%20mistakes...%20she%20doesn't%20even%20talk%20with%20respect.%20Many%20students%20complained%20but%20the%20principal%20did%20not%20listen%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20intensity%20of%20the%20protests%20prompted%20a%20visit%20from%20the%20Director%20of%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20government's%20Education%20Department%2C%20who%20sent%20Varsha%20Jha%20on%20indefinite%20leave.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20were%20also%20summoned.%20Mayur%20Khandelwal%2C%20the%20Assistant%20Commissioner%20of%20Police%20for%20Habibganj%2C%20told%20NDTV%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20were%20informed%20of%20protests%20by%20girl%20students%20that%20could%20lead%20to%20a%20law-and-order%20situation.%20A%20team%20was%20sent%20to%20calm%20things%20down%20and%20persuade%20the%20girls%20to%20end%20the%20protest.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20this%20has%20kicked%20up%20a%20predictable%20political%20row%2C%20with%20the%20opposition%20Congress'%20youth%20wing%20chief%20Mitendra%20Singh%2C%20hitting%20out%20at%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20and%20its%20'%3Cem%3Ebeti%20bachao%2C%20beti%20padhao%3C%2Fem%3E'%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENDTV%20is%20now%20available%20on%20WhatsApp%20channels.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whatsapp.com%2Fchannel%2F0029Va4lixw7z4kcvZI9JM12%5C%22%3EClick%20on%20the%20link%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20get%20all%20the%20latest%20updates%20from%20NDTV%20on%20your%20chat.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725448800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fhboqnnqg_madhya-pradesh-school-girls-protest_625x300_04_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmadhya-pradesh-sarojini-naidu-girls-school-protests-in-bhopal-girls-rise-up-in-protest-over-harsh-school-punishments-6489158%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Students%