avakhilesh)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fyadavakhilesh%2Fstatus%2F1831278052040421598%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%204%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20in%20your%20current%20situation%2C%20even%20if%20you%20are%20in%20the%20BJP%2C%20it%20(a%20tilt%20at%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20post)%20is%20as%20good%20as%20a%20'no'%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20will%20have%20to%20form%20a%20separate%20party...%20if%20not%20today%20then%20tomorrow.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EYadav%20Kickstarts%20Bulldozer%20Battle%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20squabble%20broke%20after%20Mr%20Yadav's%20gibe%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20soon%20as%20BJP%20is%20wiped%20out%20(in%20UP%20after%20the%20Assembly%20election)%20and%20the%20Samajwadi%20government%20is%20formed%2C%20the%20bulldozers%20of%20the%20entire%20state%20will%20head%20towards%20Gorakhpur%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20opposition%20leader%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhow-can-house-be-demolished-because-top-court-on-bulldozer-justice-6471609%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BHow%20Can%20House%20Be%20Demolished...%26quot%3B%20Court%20On%20'Bulldozer%20Justice'%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAkhilesh%20Yadav's%20'bulldozer'%20digs%20came%20hours%20after%20a%20key%20observation%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20questioned%20the%20idea%20of%20'bulldozer%20justice'%20and%20wanted%20to%20know%20how%20a%20building%20could%20be%20demolished%20simply%20because%20it%20belongs%20to%20an%20accused%2C%20or%20even%20a%20convict%2C%20in%20a%20criminal%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20observation%20was%20significant%20given%20the%20frequency%20with%20which%20BJP-ruled%20states%20bulldozed%20buildings%20of%20individuals%20accused%20in%20criminal%20cases%3B%20recent%20examples%20cited%20in%20court%20included%20the%20demolition%20a%20home%20in%20Rajasthan's%20Jaipur%20because%20the%20owner's%20son%20had%20stabbed%20a%20classmate.%20A%20bench%20of%20Justice%20BR%20Gavai%20and%20Justice%20KV%20Viswanathan%20took%20a%20dim%20view%20of%20the%20controversial%20practice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BIs%20Land%20For%20His%20Residence%20Approved%3F%26quot%3B%20Yadav's%20Jibe%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20afternoon%20Mr%20Yadav%20followed%20up%20Tuesday's%20jab%20with%20a%20pointed%20question%20at%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20government%2C%20demanding%20an%20apology%20from%20the%20state%20for%20houses%20and%20buildings%20bulldozed%20till%20now%2C%20and%20suggested%20the%20BJP%20change%20its%20name%20to%20Bhartiya%20Jogi%20Party.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20so%20many%20names%20(of%20cities%20and%20towns%20in%20UP)%20have%20been%20changed%2C%20then%20Chief%20Minister%20should%20change%20name%20of%20Bhartiya%20Janata%20Party%20too...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAkhilesh%20Yadav%20also%20threw%20in%20a%20cheeky%20side-swipe%20by%20asking%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20if%20the%20land%20on%20which%20his%20home%20has%20been%20built%20meets%20regulatory%20requirements.%20%26quot%3BThe%20people%20who%20scared%20others%20away%20with%20bulldozers...%20who%20demolished%20others%20houses...%20tell%20me%2C%20is%20the%20land%20for%20his%20residence%20approved%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20deliberately%20ran%20the%20bulldozer%20over%20(buildings%20belonging%20to)%20people%20from%20whom%20you%20wanted%20to%20revenge...%20to%20humiliate%20them.%20But%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20said%20a%20bulldozer%20cannot%20be%20used...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20will%20the%20government%20apologise%20for%20bulldozer%20ops%20going%20on%20till%20now%20or%20not%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20input%20from%20agencies%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENDTV%20is%20now%20available%20on%20Whats