%20say%20on%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20satisfied%20with%20the%20arrest%20of%20the%20five%20men%20as%20there%20is%20nothing%20left%20for%20me%20in%20Faridabad.%20I%20want%20to%20return%20to%20my%20native%20place.%20But%20there%20are%20many%20questions%20which%20can%20only%20be%20answered%20by%20my%20landlord's%20family.%20My%20son%20was%20taken%20towards%20Palwal%20in%20a%20car%20by%20Sujata%20Gulati%20and%20his%20sons%20Harshit%20and%20Shanky%20Gulati.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShanky%20was%20involved%20in%20a%20case%20of%20attempted%20murder%20and%20might%20have%20some%20dispute%20with%20someone%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Mishra%20also%20asked%20if%20his%20son%20was%20indeed%20shot%20by%20cow%20vigilantes%2C%20who%20gave%20them%20the%20right%20to%20do%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnil%20Kaushik%20told%20police%20that%20my%20son%20was%20killed%20because%20they%20mistook%20him%20for%20a%20cattle%20smuggler%2C%20and%20if%20he%20is%20right%2C%20who%20gave%20the%20right%20to%20cow%20vigilantes%20the%20right%20to%20shoot%20anyone%3F%20My%20son%20will%20not%20come%20back%20but%20this%20matter%20needs%20to%20be%20investigated%20seriously%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Aryan's%20brother%20has%20started%20a%20Whatsapp%20group%20%26quot%3BNyay%26quot%3B%20to%20seek%20justice%20in%20the%20killing.%20The%20group%2C%20created%20Tuesday%20night%2C%20has%20been%20joined%20by%20more%20than%201%2C000%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20police%20sources%2C%20the%20accused%20during%20interrogation%20claimed%20that%20on%20the%20night%20of%20August%2023%2C%20they%20had%20received%20information%20that%20some%20suspected%20cattle%20smugglers%20driving%20two%20SUVs%20were%20doing%20recce%20in%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20mistook%20Aryan%2C%20and%20his%20friends%2C%20Shanky%20and%20Harshit%2C%20for%20cattle%20smugglers%20and%20followed%20their%20car%20for%20about%2030%20kilometres%20near%20the%20Gadhpuri%20Toll%20on%20the%20Delhi-Agra%20National%20Highway%2C%20police%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20they%20asked%20the%20boy%20and%20his%20friends%20to%20stop%20their%20car%2C%20the%20driver%20started%20speeding%2C%20following%20which%20they%20opened%20fire%20and%20Mishra%20was%20killed%20on%20the%20spot%20near%20the%20Gadhpuri%20toll%20in%20Palwal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20arrested%20five%20men%20on%20August%2028%20and%20remanded%20them%20to%20police%20custody%20for%20two%20days%2C%20Assistant%20Commissioner%20of%20Police%20(Crime)%20Aman%20Yadav%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHemendra%20Kumar%20Meena%2C%20DCP%20crime%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BMany%20aspects%20of%20this%20case%20are%20still%20unresolved.%20The%20facts%20that%20came%20to%20light%20during%20the%20interrogation%20of%20the%20accused%20are%20being%20verified.%20The%20case%20is%20being%20investigated%20thoroughly%20and%20it%20would%20be%20premature%20to%20say%20anything%20right%20now.%20The%20police%20will%20soon%20reveal%20the%20case.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725444900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fqanrui8o_aryan-mishra_625x300_03_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmy-son-wasnt-alone-why-no-one-else-hurt-asks-father-of-student-shot-dead-by-cow-vigilantes-6488662%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20father%20of%20teenager%20Aryan%20Mishra%2C%20who%20was%20shot%20dead%20allegedly%20by%20cow%20vigilantes%20in%20a%20car%20chase%20in%20Faridabad%2C%20is%20restless%20with%20many%20questions%20about%20the%20death%2C%20such%20as%20why%20none%20of%20the%20other%20passengers%20in%20the%20vehicle%20were%20hurt%20in%20the%20attack.%22%2C%22author%22