s%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fboko-haram-militants-on-motorcycles-attacked-a-nigerian-village-killing-over-100-residents-say%2Famp_articleshow%2F113061165.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Dhoom-Style%20Heist%2C%20Man%20Steals%20Rs%2015%20Crore%20Gold%2C%20Falls%20While%20Escaping%2C%20Caught%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EInspired%20by%20Hrithik%20Roshan's%20character%20in%20Bollywood%20film%20%3Cem%3E'Dhoom%202'%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20man%20in%20Bhopal%20allegedly%20attempted%20to%20steal%20gold%20worth%20Rs%2015%20crore%20from%20a%20museum.%20But%20in%20a%20bizarre%20twist%2C%20the%20thief%20was%20discovered%20unconscious%20inside%20the%20State%20Museum%20in%20Bhopal%2C%20with%20priceless%20artifacts%20like%20ancient%20gold%20coins%20and%20jewelry%20lying%20beside%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVinod%20Yadav%2C%20believed%20to%20be%20a%20professional%20thief%2C%20had%20entered%20the%20museum%20with%20a%20ticket%20on%20Sunday%20evening%20and%20managed%20to%20hide%20inside%20until%20the%20museum%20closed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20museum%20remained%20closed%20on%20Monday%2C%20during%20which%20police%20believe%20Yadav%20broke%20into%20the%20two%20gallery%20rooms%20and%20stole%20the%20artifacts.%20When%20the%20museum%20reopened%20at%2010.30%20am%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20the%20staff%20discovered%20shattered%20glass%20and%20several%20valuable%20items%20missing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecurity%20personnel%20immediately%20began%20to%20search%20of%20the%20premises.%20During%20the%20search%2C%20they%20found%20Vinod%20Yadav%20lying%20unconscious%20in%20the%20hallway%2C%20near%20a%20large%20bag%20filled%20with%20stolen%20artifacts.%20The%20bag%20contained%20gold%20coins%20from%20the%20Gupta%20period%2C%20along%20with%20other%20items%20from%20the%20British%20and%20Nawab%20eras%2C%20including%20jewelry%20and%20utensils.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInvestigations%20suggest%20that%20Yadav%20may%20have%20fallen%20from%20a%20height%20of%20over%2023%20feet%20while%20attempting%20to%20escape%2C%20resulting%20in%20an%20injury%20to%20his%20leg.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20accused%20seems%20to%20have%20tried%20to%20jump%20over%20the%20wall%2C%20but%20failed%2C%20leading%20to%20his%20injury%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Deputy%20Commissioner%20of%20Police%20(DCP)%20Riyaz%20Iqbal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20over%2050%20fingerprints%20were%20collected%20from%20the%20museum.%20Police%20are%20exploring%20the%20possibility%20of%20an%20accomplice%20outside%20the%20museum.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20recovered%20items%20are%20gold%20coins%20weighing%20between%2050%20to%20100%20grams%20each%2C%20estimated%20to%20be%20worth%20Rs%208%20to%2010%20crore.%20DCP%20Iqbal%20said%20that%20the%20total%20value%20of%20the%20recovered%20goods%20could%20be%20around%20Rs%2015%20crore%2C%20emphasising%20that%20these%20items%20were%20taken%20from%20just%20two%20rooms%20in%20the%20museum.%20%26quot%3BThe%20entire%20museum%20houses%20artifacts%20worth%20more%20than%20Rs%2050%20crore%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20has%20raised%20serious%20concerns%20about%20the%20security%20arrangements%20at%20the%20State%20Museum%20including%20the%20lack%20of%20an%20alarm%20system%20and%20the%20fact%20that%20many%20of%20the%20CCTV%20cameras%20were%20non-functional.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20museum's%20doors%2C%20made%20of%20aluminum%2C%20were%20found%20to%20be%20weak%2C%20and%20parts%20of%20the%20roof%20were%20covered%20with%20easily%20breakable%20plastic%20sheets.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20these%20shortcomings%2C%20the%20alertness%20of%20the%20security%20guards%20played%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20preventing%20the%20theft.%20The%20accused%20reportedly%20confessed%20that%20he%20had%20attempted%20to%20escape%20several%20times%20but%20was%20forced%20to%20retreat%20due%20to%20the%20constant%20patrolling%20by%20the%20guards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20police%20team%20has%20been%20dispatched%20to%20Yadav's%20home%20in%20Bihar's%20Gaya%20to%20further%20investigate%20his%20background%20and%20possible%20connections.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725444360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fv5av0n8_bhopal-museum-theft_625x300_04_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbhopal-news%2Fin-dhoom-2-heist-man-steals-rs-15-crore-gold-falls-while-escaping-caught-6488251%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Inspired%20by%20Hrithik%20Roshan's%20character%20in%20Bollywood%20film%20%26quot%3BDhoom%202%26quot%3B%2C%20a%20young%20man%20in%20Bhopal%20allegedly%20attempted%20to%20steal%20gold%20worth%20Rs%2015%20crore%20from%20a%20museum.%20But%20in%20a%20bizarre%20twist%2C%20the%20thief%20was%20discovered%20unconscious%20inside%20the%20State%20Museum%20in%20Bhopa%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbhopal-news%2Fin-dhoom-2-heist-man-steals-rs-15-crore-gold-falls-while-escaping-caught-6488251%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ukraine's%20foreign%20minister%20resigns%20as%20government%20reshuffle%20expected%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725443941000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F87fa%2Flive%2F98d7cff0-6a46-11ef-bd4a-4fab9ce70dbc.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcn02v5x5expo%231%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20parliamentary%20head%20of%20the%20ruling%20party%20says%20half%20the%20cabinet%20will%20be%20replaced%20in%20a%20reshuffle%20this%20week.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A32%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcn02v5x5expo%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcn02v5x5expo.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcn02v5x5expo.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%