F1920x1080%2Fskynews-mestalla-valencia-barcelona_6676376.jpg%3F20240904110351%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fenglish-football-will-face-enormous-opposition-over-dynamic-pricing-as-two-spanish-sides-adopt-controversial-system-13209461%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22English%20football%20clubs%20are%20being%20warned%20they%20will%20face%20%26quot%3Benormous%20opposition%26quot%3B%20if%20they%20try%20to%20introduce%20dynamic%20pricing%20for%20match%20tickets%20-%20after%20two%20top%20sides%20in%20Spain%20confirmed%20they%20were%20adopting%20the%20controversial%20practice.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A19%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fenglish-football-will-face-enormous-opposition-over-dynamic-pricing-as-two-spanish-sides-adopt-controversial-system-13209461%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fenglish-football-will-face-enormous-opposition-over-dynamic-pricing-as-two-spanish-sides-adopt-controversial-system-13209461%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fenglish-football-will-face-enormous-opposition-over-dynamic-pricing-as-two-spanish-sides-adopt-controversial-system-13209461%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22All%20About%20PresVu%2C%20New%20Eye%20Drops%20That%20Can%20Remove%20Reading%20Glasses%20In%2015%20Mins%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Drugs%20Controller%20General%20of%20India%20has%20approved%20Entod%20Pharmaceuticals'%20PresVu%20eye%20drops%2C%20which%20is%20said%20to%20be%20a%20breakthrough%20in%20the%20treatment%20of%20presbyopia.%20The%20pharmaceutical%20company%20has%20already%20received%20approval%20for%20the%20eye%20drop%20from%20the%20Subject%20Expert%20Committee%20of%20the%20Central%20Drugs%20Standard%20Control%20Organization%20(CDSCO).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresVu%20is%20India's%20first%20eye%20drop%2C%20specially%20made%20for%20individuals%20suffering%20from%20presbyopia%20who%20are%20forced%20to%20read%20with%20glasses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Is%20Presbyopia%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresbyopia%20is%20an%20age-related%20condition%20that%20makes%20it%20difficult%20to%20focus%20on%20near%20objects.%20Generally%2C%20people%20above%2040%20years%20of%20age%20suffer%20from%20this%20condition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%2C%201.09%20billion%20to%201.80%20billion%20people%20globally%20are%20estimated%20to%20be%20suffering%20from%20presbyopia%2C%20highlighting%20the%20massive%20impact%20of%20this%20condition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresbyopia%20occurs%20naturally%20with%20ageing%20as%20the%20eye's%20ability%20to%20focus%20declines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20condition%20can%20have%20a%20significant%20impact%20on%20a%20person's%20quality%20of%20life%2C%20affecting%20their%20ability%20to%20perform%20everyday%20tasks%20and%20maintain%20their%20lifestyle.%20Many%20realise%20they%20have%20presbyopia%20when%20they%20try%20to%20hold%20reading%20objects%20at%20arm's%20length%20to%20see%20clearly.%20It%20can%20be%20detected%20by%20a%20simple%20examination%20of%20the%20eyes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20PresVu%2C%20Nikhil%20K%20Masurkar%2C%20CEO%2C%20Entod%20Pharmaceuticals%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BPresVu%20has%20been%20created%20through%20years%20of%20research%20and%20development.%20Its%20approval%20by%20DCGI%20is%20a%20major%20step%20in%20our%20mission%20to%20transform%20eye%20care%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPresVu%3A%20Key%20Benefits%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEntod%20Pharmaceuticals%20has%20applied%20for%20a%20patent%20regarding%20the%20formulation%20and%20process%20of%20PresVu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEntod's%20formula%20not%20only%20provides%20relief%20from%20reading%20glasses%20but%20also%20gives%20an%20additional%20benefit%20to%20the%20patient%20--%20it%20helps%20lubricate%20the%20eyes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20formula%20uses%20advanced%20dynamic%20buffer%20technology%20to%20rapidly%20adapt%20to%20the%20pH%20of%20tears.%20Its%20effect%20remains%20for%20a%20longer%20duration%2C%20while%20the%20eyes%20also%20remain%20protected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENikkhil%20K%20Masurkar%2C%20CEO%2C%20Entod%20Pharmaceuticals%20noted%20that%20PresVu%20was%20created%20after%20years%20of%20research%20and%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20DCGI%20approval%20is%20a%20major%20step%20forward%20in%20our%20mission%20to%20transform%20eye%20care%20in%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMasurkar%20noted%20that%20PresVu%20is%20more%20than%20just%20a%20product%3B%20it's%20a%20solution%20that%20works%20to%20improve%20the%20lives%20of%20millions%20of%20people%20by%20helping%20them%20see%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Enhances%20Near%20Vision%20In%2015%20minutes'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHighlighting%20the%20benefits%20of%20PresVu%20for%20patients%2C%20Dr%20Aditya%20Sethi%20noted%20that%20Presbyopia%20has%20long%20been%20treated%20with%20reading%20glasses%2C%20contact%20lenses%20and%20surgical%20measures.%20With%20PresVu%2C%20it%20can%20be%20treated%20effectively%20as%20the%20eye%20drop%20improves%20near%20vision%20within%2015%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20treatment%20can%20significantly%20improve%20the%20quality%20of%20life%20for%20many%20people%2C%20allowing%20them%20to%20perform%20everyday%20tasks%20easily%2C%20he%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20doctor%20further%20noted%20that%20it%20was%20important%20to%20monitor%20symptoms%20and%20consult%20a%20doctor%20if%20blurred%20near%20vision%20interferes%20with%20reading%20or%20other%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommenting%20on%20the%20clinical%20potential%20of%20PresVu%2C%20Dr%20Dhananjay%20Bakhle%20said%20its%20approval%20was%20a%20promising%20achievement%20in%20the%20field%20of%20ophthalmology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20presbyopia%20patients%2C%20this%20eye%20drop%20provides%20a%20non-invasive%20option%20that%20eliminates%20the%20need%20for%20reading%20glasses%2C%20he%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725443040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2F4lq6keso_eye-drop-generic_625x300_04_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fall-about-presvu-new-eye-drops-that-can-remove-reading-glasses-in-15-mins-6488271%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Drugs%20Controller%20General%20of%20India%20has%20approved%20Entod%20Pharmaceuticals'%20PresVu%20eye%20drops%2C%20which%20is%20said%20to%20be%20a%20breakthrough%20in%20the%20treatment%20of%20presbyopia.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fall-about-presvu-new-eye-drops-that-can-remove-reading-glasses-in-15-mins-6488271%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Workers%20see%20dramatic%20fall%20in%20share%20of%20global%20income%3A%20UN%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725442614000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-113060040%2Cimgsize-1245776.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fworkers-see-dramatic-fall-in-share-of-global-income-un%2Farticleshow%2F113059967.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F113059967.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20UN's%20International%20Labour%20Organization%20states%20that%20the%20global%20labour%20income%20share%20has%20fallen%20by%201.6%25%20since%202004%2C%20causing%20a%20%242.4%20trillion%20annual%20shortfall%20for%20workers.%20This%20decline%2C%20intensified%20by%20the%20Covid-19%20pandemic%2C%20highlights%20rising%20inequality%20and%20underscores%20the%20need%20for%20policies%20to%20ensure%20fair%20economic%20distribution.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22http