%2016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBajaj%20Housing%20Finance%20IPO%20offer%20size%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bajaj%20Housing%20Finance%20IPO%20is%20a%20book-built%20issue%20of%20%E2%82%B96%2C560%20crore.%20It%20comprises%20an%20offer%20for%20sale%20(OFS)%20component%20of%2042.86%20crore%20equity%20shares%20by%20parent%20company%20Bajaj%20Finance%20worth%20%E2%82%B93%2C000%20crore%2C%20and%20a%20fresh%20issue%20of%2050.86%20crore%20shares%20totalling%20%E2%82%B93%2C560%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBajaj%20Housing%20Finance%20IPO%20lot%20size%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minimum%20lot%20size%20for%20application%20in%20Bajaj%20Housing%20Finance%20IPO%20is%20214%20shares%2C%20totalling%20an%20investment%20of%20%E2%82%B914%2C980%20at%20the%20upper%20price%20band.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBajaj%20Housing%20Finance%20IPO%20objectives%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20main%20purpose%20of%20the%20Bajaj%20Housing%20Finance%20IPO%20is%20to%20fulfil%20a%20mandate%20from%20the%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%20(RBI)%2C%20which%20requires%20top%20non-banking%20financial%20organisations%20(NBFCs)%20to%20get%20listed%20on%20the%20stock%20markets%20within%20three%20years%20of%20getting%20an%20%26quot%3Bupper%20layer%26quot%3B%20status.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBajaj%20Housing%20Finance%20Limited%20will%20use%20the%20net%20proceeds%20from%20the%20fresh%20issue%20to%20augment%20its%20capital%20base%20to%20meet%20future%20business%20requirements%20towards%20onward%20lending.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBajaj%20Housing%20Finance%20IPO%20other%20key%20details%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20has%20appointed%20KFin%20Technologies%20Limited%20as%20the%20registrar%20for%20the%20public%20issue.%20Kotak%20Mahindra%20Capital%20Company%20Ltd%2C%20Axis%20Capital%20Ltd%2C%20BofA%20Securities%20India%20Ltd%2C%20SBI%20Capital%20Markets%20Ltd%2C%20JM%20Financial%20Ltd%2C%20Goldman%20Sachs%20(India)%20Securities%20Private%20Ltd%2C%20and%20IIFL%20Securities%20Ltd.%20are%20the%20book-running%20lead%20managers%20for%20Bajaj%20Housing%20Finance%20IPO.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725442560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fea9vi27o_housing-generic-_625x300_04_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbajaj-housing-finance-ipo-price-band-at-66-to-70-per-share-all-you-need-to-know-6488210%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Bajaj%20Housing%20Finance%20IPO%20is%20a%20book-built%20issue%20of%20%E2%82%B96%2C560%20crore.%20It%20comprises%20an%20offer%20for%20sale%20(OFS)%20component%20of%2042.86%20crore%20equity%20shares%20worth%20%E2%82%B93%2C000%20crore%20and%20a%20fresh%20issue%20of%2050.86%20crore%20shares%20totalling%20%E2%82%B93%2C560%20crore.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbajaj-housing-finance-ipo-price-band-at-66-to-70-per-share-all-you-need-to-know-6488210%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sodomy%2C%20Lesbianism%20Unnatural%20Offences%3A%20New%20Textbook%20For%20Medical%20Students%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESodomy%20or%20being%20a%20lesbian%20is%20an%20unnatural%20sex%20offence%2C%20says%20the%20latest%20textbook%20introduced%20by%20National%20Medical%20Commission%20for%20undergraduate%20medical%20students.%20The%20revised%20curriculum%20also%20includes%20discussions%20on%20sexual%20perversions%2C%20fetishism%2C%20and%20other%20topics%2C%20but%20has%20removed%20distinctions%20between%20consensual%20sex%20between%20queer%20individuals%2C%20reports%20the%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20changes%20have%20been%20introduced%20in%20the%20forensic%20medicine%20and%20toxicology%20textbook%20for%20undergraduate%20students.%20These%20subjects%20were%20previously%20removed%20in%202022%20following%20a%20Madras%20High%20Court%20directive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20amended%20curriculum%20has%20also%20brought%20back%20topics%20such%20as%20the%20hymen%20and%20its%20type%2C%20and%20its%20medico-legal%20importance%20besides%20defining%20virginity%20and%20defloration%2C%20legitimacy%20and%20its%20medico-legal%20importance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20controversial%20textbook%20also%20includes%20sexual%20perversions%2C%20fetishism%2C%20sadism%2C%20voyeurism%2C%20exhibitionism%2C%20transvestism%2C%20and%20necrophilia.%20However%2C%20there%20is%20no%20mention%20of%20consensual%20sex%20between%20queer%20individuals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20amended%20curriculum%20has%20done%20away%20with%20the%20seven-hour%20training%20on%20disability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Commission%20claims%20the%20changes%20are%20part%20of%20an%20outcome-driven%20curriculum%20aligned%20with%20global%20trends%2C%20aiming%20to%20create%20an%20%26quot%3BIndian%20medical%20graduate%26quot%3B%20with%20requisite%20knowledge%2C%20skills%2C%20and%20values.%20However%2C%20critics%20argue%20that%20the%20reintroduction%20of%20these%20topics%20may%20perpetuate%20harmful%20attitudes%20towards%20marginalized%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20time%20to%20have%20a%20relook%20at%20all%20aspects%20of%20the%20various%20components%20in%20the%20existing%20regulations%20and%20guidelines%2C%20and%20adapt%20them%20to%20the%20changing%20demography%2C%20socio-economic%20context%2C%20perceptions%2C%20values%2C%20advancements%20in%20medical%20education%20and%20expectations%20of%20stakeholders%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20NMC%20said%20in%20its%20Competency-Based%20Medical%20Education%20Curriculum%20(CBME)%20Guidelines%2C%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20revised%20curriculum%20also%20focuses%20on%20medico-legal%20frameworks%2C%20codes%20of%20conduct%2C%20and%20medical%20ethics%2C%20with%20an%20emphasis%20on%20alignment%20and%20integration%20of%20subjects.%20The%20commission%20said%20it%20aims%20to%20produce%20a%20primary%20care%20physician%20with%20skills%20in%20promotive%2C%20preventative%2C%20rehabilitative%2C%20palliative%20care%2C%20and%20referral%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20first%20contact%20physician%20needs%20to%20be%20skilful%20to%20perform%20duties%20of%20primary%20care%20physician%20and%20have%20requisite%20skills%20for%20promotive%2C%20preventative%2C%20rehabilitative%2C%20palliative%20care%20and%20referral%20services%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20document%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20has%20raised%20concerns%20among%20medical%20professionals%20and%20LGBTQ%2B%20advocates%2C%20who%20argue%20that%20the%20changes%20may%20undermine%20progress%20made%20in%20promoting%20inclusivity%20and%20understanding%20in%20medical%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725442260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fcqbl6u5g_medical-student-generic_625x300_04_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsodomy-lesbianism-are-unnatural-sex-offences-new-textbook-for-medical-students-6488265%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sodomy%20or%20being%20a%20lesbian%20is%20an%20unnatural%20sex%20offence%2C%20says%20the%20latest%20textbook%20introduced%20by%20National%20Medical%20Commission%20for%20undergraduate%20medical%20students.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsodomy-lesbianism-are-unnatural-sex-offences-new-textbook-for-medical-students-6488265%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ganesh%20Chaturthi%3A%20Top%208%20Places%20For%20The%20Best%20Modak%20in%20Mumbai%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20time%20for%20Ganesh%20Chaturthi%20again%2C%20when%20everyone%20celebrates%20the%20elephant-headed%20God.%20Celebrated%20throughout%20the%20country%2C%20the%20names%20may%20change%2C%20from%20Ganesha%20to%20Vinayaka%20to%20Ganapati%20to%20Pillaiyar%2C%20but%20one%20thing%20remains%20constant%20%E2%80%93%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20no