2C%20believing%20Pavithra%20Gowda%20had%20destroyed%20Darshan's%20family%20life%20and%20targeted%20her%20in%20support%20of%20his%20wife.%20Renukaswamy%20had%20allegedly%20sent%20a%20photograph%20of%20his%20genitals%20to%20Pavithra%20Gowda%20and%20claimed%20that%20he%20was%20better%20than%20Darshan%2C%20according%20to%20the%20sources.%20He%20Renukaswamy%20also%20continued%20sending%20derogatory%20messages%20to%20Pavithra%20Gowda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20able%20to%20take%20the%20torture%2C%20Pavithra%20Gowda%20had%20informed%20Darshan's%20close%20associate%20Pavan%20and%20asked%20him%20to%20handle%20the%20situation%20without%20informing%20the%20superstar%2C%20sources%20said.%20However%2C%20Pavan%20had%20shared%20the%20information%20with%20Darshan.%20Enraged%20by%20this%2C%20Darshan%20had%20tasked%20Pavan%20to%20find%20out%20who%20this%20person%20tormenting%20her%20was%20and%20bring%20him%20before%20him.%20Pavan%20had%20allegedly%20started%20chatting%20to%20Renukaswamy%20in%20the%20guise%20of%20Pavithra%20Gowda%20and%20started%20gathering%20information%20about%20him%20and%20his%20movements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20tracking%20down%20Renukaswamy%2C%20another%20accused%2C%20Raghavendra%2C%20the%20President%20of%20the%20Darshan%20Fan%20Club%20Association%20of%20Chitradurga%2C%20was%20roped%20into%20kidnap%20him.%20Renukaswamy%20was%20asked%20to%20come%20to%20Bengaluru%20and%20accused%20Pavan%20and%20Raghavendra%20assured%20him%20that%20all%20he%20had%20to%20do%20was%20to%20apologise%20to%20Darshan%20for%20what%20he%20did%20and%20he%20would%20be%20let%20off.%20They%20also%20promised%20him%20selfies%20with%20Darshan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Renukaswamy%20was%20undecided%2C%20the%20accused%20forced%20him%20to%20board%20an%20auto%20and%20later%20forcefully%20took%20him%20into%20a%20vehicle%20from%20the%20outskirts%20of%20Chitradurga%20city.%20He%20was%20later%20taken%20to%20a%20shed%20in%20Rajarajeshwari%20Nagar%20locality%20in%20Bengaluru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDarshan%20was%20then%20informed%20that%20Renukaswamy%20had%20been%20brought%20there%2C%20came%20to%20the%20shed%20with%20Pavithra%20Gowda%2C%20and%20allegedly%20started%20assaulting%20him%2C%20along%20with%20his%20gang%2C%20for%20hours.%20The%20gang%20had%20brought%20a%20device%20for%20giving%20electric%20shocks%20and%20allegedly%20subjected%20the%20abducted%20fan%20to%20repeated%20shocks%20to%20his%20genitals.%20He%20was%20also%20flung%20against%20trucks%20parked%20in%20the%20shed%20and%20kicked%20around%20like%20a%20football.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERenukaswamy%20was%20fed%20non-vegetarian%20food%20even%20as%20he%20pleaded%20with%20them%20that%20he%20was%20a%20vegetarian.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDetailing%20the%20further%20torture%20he%20underwent%2C%20sources%20said%20that%20Renukaswamy%20was%20burnt%20at%20various%20parts%20of%20his%20body%20and%20even%20as%20he%20bled%20profusely%2C%20the%20gang%20continued%20to%20assault%20him%20throughout%20the%20night%20after%20taking%20breaks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20also%20that%20the%20accused%20consumed%20liquor%20and%20other%20substances%20as%20they%20unleashed%20unheard%20brutalities%20on%20him.%20As%20Renukaswamy%20succumbed%20to%20his%20injuries%2C%20Darshan%20and%20the%20gang%20allegedly%20planned%20to%20dispose%20of%20the%20body%20and%20make%20four%20persons%20surrender%20to%20the%20police%20claiming%20that%20they%20hacked%20Renukaswamy%20to%20death%20over%20a%20financial%20matter.%20However%2C%20the%20police%20officers%20managed%20to%20crack%20the%20case%20and%20get%20information%20about%20the%20kidnapping%20and%20the%20brutal%20murder%20of%20Renukaswamy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERenukaswamy%20hailed%20from%20a%20middle-class%20background%20with%20his%20father%20Kashinatha%20Shivanagoudara%20being%20a%20retired%20government%20employee.%20Working%20at%20a%20pharmacy%20store%2C%20he%20was%20the%20sole%20breadwinner%20for%20the%20family%20and%20had%20a%20pregnant%20wife.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this