y.%20She%20was%20my%20everything.%20But%20then%20my%20mental%20situation%20worsened%20after%20her%20death.%20I%20sunk%20into%20darkness%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20friends%20and%20badminton%20helped%20pull%20him%20away%20from%20the%20dark%20place.%20He%20decided%20to%20do%20his%20best%20and%20started%20working%20on%20defending%20his%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F337854%2Fsheetal-devi-arjuna-award-para-archery-first-armless-female-archer-jammu-kashmir%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EParalympic%20gold%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Paris.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20eyes%20are%20on%20Krishna%20as%20we%20look%20forward%20to%20a%20potential%20repeat%20of%20his%20Tokyo%20success%20in%20Paris.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESources%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsportstar.thehindu.com%2Folympics%2Fparis-paralympics-2024%2Fnews%2Fparis-paralympics-2024-krishna-nagar-gold-medal-defence-badminton-indian-athletes%2Farticle68562213.ece%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Paris%202024%3A%20With%20one%20eye%20on%20defending%20Paralympics%20title%2C%20Krishna%20Nagar%20banks%20on%20tight-knit%20Indian%20contingent%20for%20support%E2%80%99%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3Eby%20Aditya%20Padinjat%2C%20Published%20on%2024%20August%202024%2C%20Courtesy%20Sportstar%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fsport%2Fother%2F2021%2FSep%2F05%2Fkrishna-nagar-wins-gold-in-mens-badminton-singles-sh6-class-at-tokyo-paralympics-2354582.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Once%20bullied%20for%20s