and%20more.%20With%20over%20200%20plants%20thriving%20in%20grow%20bags%2C%20the%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F348771%2Fgrow-organic-food-doctor-naveen-kumar-farming-workshop-chennai-vegetables-fruits-at-home-gardening%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20terrace%20garden%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20become%20a%20constant%20source%20of%20joy%20and%20sustenance%20for%20Padma%3B%20and%20also%20a%20link%20to%20her%20rural%20roots.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20only%20have%20to%20purchase%20potatoes%2C%20garlic%2C%20tamarind%2C%20and%20onions%20from%20the%20market.%20Other%20than%20these%20vegetables%2C%20my%20terrace%20garden%20supplies%20all%20the%20basic%20produce%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20points%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fpadma-suresh-1-1724831341.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Padma%20grows%20veggies%20such%20as%20chillies%2C%20tomatoes%2C%20beans%2C%20brinjals%2C%20curry%20leaves%2C%20cauliflowers%2C%20okra%2C%20and%20more.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fpadma-suresh-1-1724831341.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fpadma-suresh-1-1724831341-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fpadma-suresh-1-1724831341-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fpadma-suresh-1-1724831341-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fpadma-suresh-1-1724831341-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-363156%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EPadma%20grows%20veggies%20such%20as%20chillies%2C%20tomatoes%2C%20beans%2C%20brinjals%2C%20curry%20leaves%2C%20cauliflowers%2C%20okra%2C%20and%20more.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20vegetables%20from%20her%20terrace%20are%20sufficient%20to%20provide%20for%20her%20family%20of%20four%2C%20Padma%20sells%20the%20extra%20harvest%20in%20the%20market.%20So%2C%20growing%20vegetables%20is%20not%20just%20a%20mere%20hobby%20for%20her%20but%20also%20a%20mode%20of%20income.%20%E2%80%9CEvery%20Sunday%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20gardeners%20reach%20Gandhi%20Bhawan%20to%20sell%20organically%20grown%20vegetables.%20I%20too%20have%20a%20dedicated%20stall%20where%20I%20sell%20extra%20vegetables.%20Within%20an%20hour%2C%20all%20my%20vegetables%20are%20sold%20out.%20This%20organic%20farming%20business%20earns%20me%20up%20to%20Rs%201%2C000%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBy%20eliminating%20the%20need%20to%20purchase%20vegetables%20from%20the%20market%2C%20I%20have%20not%20only%20achieved%20self-sufficiency%20but%20also%20significantly%20reduced%20my%20monthly%20expenses%20on%20vegetables%20by%20saving%20around%20Rs%201%2C500%20per%20month%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPadma%20says%20with%20little%20effort%2C%20anyone%20can%20grow%20vegetables%20organically%20at%20home.%20She%20relies%20on%20natural%20fertilisers%20like%20vermicompost%2C%20cow%20dung%2C%20poultry%20dung%2C%20bonemeal%2C%20and%20neem%20cake%2C%20steering%20clear%20of%20harmful%20chemicals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20she%20employs%20innovative%20organic%20farming%20methods%20like%20preparing%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F338660%2Fhow-to-grow-fruits-on-terrace-gardening-tips-visakhapatnam-woman-wins-award%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eliquid%20fertilisers%20%3C%2Fa%3Efrom%20jaggery%20and%20fish%2C%20which%20act%20both%20as%20a%20nutrient%20source%20and%20pesticide%20for%20the%20plants.%20Sharing%20the%20technique%